544
00:31:19.125 --> 00:31:23.250
<i>♪ With your magic words ♪</i>

545
00:31:23.333 --> 00:31:27.667
<i>♪ Make me sway to your rhythm ♪</i>

546
00:31:27.750 --> 00:31:32.083
<i>♪ With just a hint from you ♪</i>

547
00:31:32.167 --> 00:31:36.500
<i>♪ Send me spinning in love ♪</i>

548
