<i>♪ With no thought of turning back ♪</i>

555
00:32:02.000 --> 00:32:04.208
Tony. I never saw you in college.

556
00:32:04.292 --> 00:32:06.417
But I saw you every day.

557
00:32:06.500 --> 00:32:08.208
The entire college would look at me.

558
00:32:08.292 --> 00:32:10.375
And Sahil Sharma used
to stare so hard.

559
00:32:11.667 --> 00:32:12.750
Sahil Sharma

560
00:32:12.833 --> 00:32:13.851
from the Commerce Department?

561
00:32:13.875 --> 00:32:15.000
You remember him?

562
00:32:15.083 --> 00:32:18.208
He spread a rumor
that you and he were dating.

563
00:32:18.625 --> 00:32:19.625
That rascal.

564
00:32:20.417 --> 00:32:21.417
You know what?

565
00:32:22.083 --> 00:32:23.417
He once wrote a love letter

566
00:32:23.958 --> 00:32:25.583
to the principal's daughter.

567
00:32:25.833 --> 00:32:28.042
And the principal threw
him out the very next day.

568
00:32:28.125 --> 00:32:29.917
- Really?
- Karma. Tony.

569
00:32:30.000 --> 00:32:31.250
He messed with Kannu Ahuja.

570
00:32:31.333 --> 00:32:33.500
Do you really think Sahil
was dumb enough for that?

571
00:32:34.083 --> 00:32:35.643
To write a letter
to the principal's daughter?

572
00:32:35.667 --> 00:32:39.417
- What do you mean?
- I mean... it wasn't Karma. Kannu.

573
00:32:39.667 --> 00:32:40.667
It was Kalra.

574
00:32:42.125 --> 00:32:43.208
Myself. Tony Kalra.

575
00:32:47.292 --> 00:32:49.417
You wrote those letters?

576
00:32:49.500 --> 00:32:50.917
He was ruining your reputation.

577
00:32:51.000 --> 00:32:52.125
I couldn't take it.

578
00:33:04.083 --> 00:33:06.167
I...

579
00:33:06.583 --> 00:33:08.125
Here you go.

580
00:33:08.208 --> 00:33:09.417
No...

581
00:33:09.500 --> 00:33:11.583
Four... five... six...

582
00:33:12.125 --> 00:33:13.125
Mom.

583
00:33:15.083 --> 00:33:16.167
we're leaving.

584
00:33:17.167 --> 00:33:18.167
What happened. Dad?

585
00:33:20.417 --> 00:33:21.708
We're going back to Delhi.

586
00:33:22.333 --> 00:33:23.458
Why? What happened?

587
00:33:23.542 --> 00:33:28.208
If we don't even deserve to know
who our mother is marrying.

588
00:33:28.292 --> 00:33:30.500
why should we stay here?

589
00:33:30.583 --> 00:33:32.792
At least introduce him to us. Grandma.

590
00:33:32.875 --> 00:33:34.417
The sooner they meet him.

591
00:33:34.500 --> 00:33:37.125
the sooner they'll get used
to calling him "Dad". Right?

592
00:33:37.208 --> 00:33:38.583
This is pointless. Tony.

593
00:33:38.667 --> 00:33:40.125
Pack your bags.

594
00:33:40.208 --> 00:33:41.708
Come. Kannu. Come on. Bittu.

595
00:33:41.792 --> 00:33:43.875
Come on. son. Let's go.

596
00:33:58.875 --> 00:34:02.250
- Hello. Shakti.
- Vimla. who are you marrying?

597
00:34:02.333 --> 00:34:03.792
At least tell your children.

598
00:34:03.875 --> 00:34:04.875
How do you know?

599
00:34:04.958 --> 00:34:07.833
Your kids came to me
looking for their "father".

600
00:34:07.917 --> 00:34:09.667
I don't know what to do.

601
00:34:09.750 --> 00:34:11.583
Just tell them his name.

602
00:34:11.667 --> 00:34:12.833
What name should I tell them?

603
00:34:14.625 --> 00:34:15.625
What?

604
00:34:15.958 --> 00:34:17.583
Have you lost your mind?

605
00:34:17.667 --> 00:34:19.292
We'll have to introduce him too.

606
00:34:19.375 --> 00:34:20.833
We'll introduce them.

607
00:34:21.208 --> 00:34:23.958
Tell them the name
and say you'll introduce them tomorrow.

608
00:34:24.375 --> 00:34:25.375
Okay.

609
00:34:36.375 --> 00:34:37.208
Dad.

610
00:34:37.292 --> 00:34:38.208
Yes.

611
00:34:38.292 --> 00:34:40.833
You all go ahead.
I'll come later.

612
00:34:41.250 --> 00:34:42.250
What does that even mean?

613
00:34:42.917 --> 00:34:44.042
No arguments.

614
00:34:44.583 --> 00:34:46.224
Pack your bags.
We're going back to Delhi.

615
00:34:49.500 --> 00:34:50.500
Jeevan!

616
00:34:50.667 --> 00:34:51.667
Naag!

617
00:34:51.875 --> 00:34:52.792
Romal!

618
00:34:52.875 --> 00:34:53.875
Baby!

619
00:34:55.292 --> 00:34:56.292
I know

620
00:34:56.917 --> 00:34:59.375
you're upset with me.

621
00:34:59.833 --> 00:35:02.375
but I won't do anything

622
00:35:02.667 --> 00:35:04.375
to embarrass you.

623
00:35:04.875 --> 00:35:06.125
Soon

624
00:35:06.417 --> 00:35:08.500
you'll understand.

625
00:35:09.042 --> 00:35:10.083
Anyway

626
00:35:10.292 --> 00:35:13.333
you want to know
your future father's name.

627
00:35:14.042 --> 00:35:15.042
His name is.

628
00:35:15.375 --> 00:35:18.750
Captain Adivishnu Reddy.

629
00:35:28.167 --> 00:35:29.167
Captain...

630
00:35:30.042 --> 00:35:31.042
Adivishnu...

631
00:35:32.292 --> 00:35:33.333
Reddy.

632
00:35:34.917 --> 00:35:36.292
According to me.

633
00:35:36.667 --> 00:35:40.000
life becomes beautiful with three C's.

634
00:35:40.375 --> 00:35:41.917
Three C's?

635
00:35:42.000 --> 00:35:45.833
Confidence. Carefulness. Cleverness.

636
00:35:47.667 --> 00:35:50.667
These are the pillars of my life.

637
00:35:51.167 --> 00:35:53.458
But shouldn't there be four?

638
00:35:53.542 --> 00:35:55.625
I am the fourth C.

639
00:35:56.667 --> 00:35:57.792
Captain.

640
00:35:59.750 --> 00:36:02.958
Tell Ms. Vimla not to worry.

641
00:36:03.333 --> 00:36:06.000
Adivishnu is with her.

642
00:36:06.083 --> 00:36:07.292
- Adivishnu.
- Yes.

643
00:36:07.375 --> 00:36:09.125
- Be at Vimla's house...
- Okay.

644
00:36:09.208 --> 00:36:11.250
- Today at eight.
- I'll be there.

645
00:36:11.333 --> 00:36:12.667
And remember.

646
00:36:12.750 --> 00:36:15.083
you've known her for six months.

647
00:36:15.167 --> 00:36:16.708
Ms. Shakti. don't worry.

648
00:36:16.792 --> 00:36:18.125
Tell Ms. Vimla

649
00:36:18.208 --> 00:36:20.292
with confidence. carefulness

650
00:36:20.375 --> 00:36:22.000
and cleverness.
I'll handle everything.

651
00:36:22.083 --> 00:36:23.875
Okay. Thank you!

652
00:36:23.958 --> 00:36:25.167
You're dealing with...

653
00:36:25.250 --> 00:36:26.792
Captain Adivishnu Reddy.

654
00:36:26.875 --> 00:36:28.555
- Thank you. sir. Thank you.
- Don't worry.

655
00:36:28.583 --> 00:36:29.583
Thank you.

656
00:36:29.667 --> 00:36:30.667
Okay.

657
00:36:30.750 --> 00:36:32.333
- You came on this?
- Bye.

658
00:36:32.417 --> 00:36:35.542
Yes. Another C in my life.

659
00:36:35.625 --> 00:36:37.792
Cycle. A bicycle.

660
00:36:45.792 --> 00:36:47.917
- Oh. my God.
- Oh. my God.

661
00:36:54.542 --> 00:36:55.833
The guy is coming tonight.

662
00:36:55.917 --> 00:36:57.792
and you're sitting here eating <i>Paratha</i>.

663
00:36:57.875 --> 00:36:59.542
Even if I were eating there.

664
00:36:59.625 --> 00:37:00.792
he would still come.

665
00:37:01.208 --> 00:37:02.458
Relax. Eat.

666
00:37:02.542 --> 00:37:04.292
I can't relax.

667
00:37:04.375 --> 00:37:06.542
My chest feels weird.

668
00:37:07.042 --> 00:37:09.167
Like palpitations.

669
00:37:09.250 --> 00:37:10.583
It's just your imagination.

670
00:37:11.792 --> 00:37:14.167
Take deep breaths.

671
00:37:15.208 --> 00:37:16.792
The rabbit is entering the lion's den.

672
00:37:16.875 --> 00:37:18.184
- Exactly.
- The rabbit should be scared.

673
00:37:18.208 --> 00:37:19.458
not the lion.

674
00:37:19.542 --> 00:37:20.583
What's going on?

675
00:37:22.042 --> 00:37:23.042
Do you want a paratha?

676
00:37:23.083 --> 00:37:24.833
- No.
- Why?

677
00:37:24.917 --> 00:37:26.458
- I just don't.
- Have some tea.

678
00:37:26.542 --> 00:37:27.708
- Not now.
- Fine. sit.

679
00:37:27.792 --> 00:37:29.417
I don't want to. Don't force me.

680
00:37:30.333 --> 00:37:31.667
How is the paratha?

681
00:37:32.125 --> 00:37:34.208
Amazing. ma'am. Loved them.

682
00:37:34.792 --> 00:37:36.875
Aren't you leaving for Delhi today?

683
00:37:37.625 --> 00:37:39.333
Should I pack some for the road?

684
00:37:39.417 --> 00:37:40.708
It's a long journey.

685
00:37:41.125 --> 00:37:42.333
You'll feel hungry on the way.

686
00:37:42.958 --> 00:37:45.167
No. ma'am.
I don't eat while traveling.

687
00:37:45.250 --> 00:37:46.917
- Why?
- I feel sick.

688
00:37:47.000 --> 00:37:49.583
- Ma'am. how are you?
- I'm good. Gaggu. You?

689
00:37:49.667 --> 00:37:50.833
I'm great. How are you?

690
00:37:50.917 --> 00:37:53.417
I'm good. Gaggu.
Please install the Wi-Fi quickly.

691
00:37:53.500 --> 00:37:54.875
The kids are getting restless.

692
00:37:54.958 --> 00:37:56.500
Yes. ma'am. The technician is here.

693
00:37:56.583 --> 00:37:58.226
He's checking the wiring.
It will be installed by today evening.

694
00:37:58.250 --> 00:37:59.083
- Are you sure?
- Yes.

695
00:37:59.167 --> 00:38:00.167
Gaggu!

696
00:38:01.000 --> 00:38:02.000
Kannu!

697
00:38:02.875 --> 00:38:04.000
How are you?

698
00:38:04.083 --> 00:38:05.208
I'm good.

699
00:38:09.333 --> 00:38:10.333
Who's he?

700
00:38:10.417 --> 00:38:11.417
Gaggu.

701
00:38:11.667 --> 00:38:13.208
Kannu's childhood friend.

702
00:38:13.792 --> 00:38:15.875
He runs a big cable business.

703
00:38:16.375 --> 00:38:17.708
Such a nice guy.

704
00:38:33.208 --> 00:38:34.208
Mr. Ahuja.

705
00:38:35.625 --> 00:38:37.625
The guy is coming tonight.

706
00:38:38.000 --> 00:38:39.351
and you're just eating paratha over here.

707
00:38:39.375 --> 00:38:42.417
Even if I were eating there.
he'd still come.

708
00:38:42.750 --> 00:38:45.792
This isn't the time to argue. sir.

709
00:38:45.875 --> 00:38:48.000
We need to deal with him.

710
00:38:48.542 --> 00:38:49.583
Our common enemy.

711
00:38:49.667 --> 00:38:51.792
We will. at the right time.

712
00:38:51.875 --> 00:38:53.625
That "right time" never comes.

713
00:38:53.708 --> 00:38:55.042
Times are bad already.

714
00:38:55.125 --> 00:38:57.208
The cable guys are driving BMWs.

715
00:38:57.792 --> 00:38:59.125
How will things be right?

716
00:38:59.375 --> 00:39:02.458
We must stop him from coming here.

717
00:39:02.542 --> 00:39:05.083
How do we find one man in Shimla?

718
00:39:05.167 --> 00:39:06.167
Sir.

719
00:39:06.542 --> 00:39:08.833
How many South Indians live in Shimla?

720
00:39:09.333 --> 00:39:12.500
And how many are named Adivishnu Reddy?

721
00:39:13.500 --> 00:39:16.208
And how many are retired army officers?

722
00:39:16.292 --> 00:39:18.583
And how many are captains?

723
00:39:18.667 --> 00:39:19.667
What are you getting at?

724
00:39:19.750 --> 00:39:20.792
Come with me.

725
00:39:21.667 --> 00:39:22.708
I know exactly

726
00:39:23.417 --> 00:39:25.000
where to find him.

727
00:39:28.917 --> 00:39:31.000
My jinx worked.

728
00:39:31.500 --> 00:39:33.458
He's broken his knee.

729
00:39:33.542 --> 00:39:36.000
It'll take at least a month
for Mr. C to recover.

730
00:39:36.083 --> 00:39:38.042
Vimla ji. no problem.

731
00:39:38.292 --> 00:39:40.208
I'll visit your house in a month.

732
00:39:41.583 --> 00:39:42.583
What now?

733
00:40:22.375 --> 00:40:23.750
Those who challenge storms

734
00:40:23.833 --> 00:40:25.809
don't look good falling off bicycles
and breaking their legs.

735
00:40:25.833 --> 00:40:27.958
You're not setting
a good example. Captain.

736
00:40:28.042 --> 00:40:31.583
I'll send your lunch and clothes
through Fateh.

737
00:40:32.083 --> 00:40:33.625
- You take good rest.
- Thank you.

738
00:40:33.708 --> 00:40:35.375
- Bye.
- Thank you. ladies. Bye.

739
00:40:39.750 --> 00:40:41.792
He's a retired colonel.

740
00:40:41.875 --> 00:40:44.250
Mr. Theeran Devarajan from Chennai.

741
00:40:44.750 --> 00:40:47.125
From 1971 to 1999.

742
00:40:47.208 --> 00:40:50.333
his bravery was talked about
in every war.

743
00:40:51.125 --> 00:40:52.458
After retirement.

744
00:40:52.542 --> 00:40:54.625
he visits Shimla every year.

745
00:40:55.125 --> 00:40:57.208
He stays at my house.

746
00:40:59.000 --> 00:41:00.375
Mr. Theeran Devarajan.

747
00:41:00.917 --> 00:41:01.958
Yes.

748
00:41:02.042 --> 00:41:03.750
I'm Shakti Kapoor.

749
00:41:04.083 --> 00:41:07.000
This is Malhotra. Chauhan and Vimla.

750
00:41:07.917 --> 00:41:10.125
We need a small favor.

751
00:41:11.625 --> 00:41:12.667
Go ahead.

752
00:41:27.750 --> 00:41:32.625
If Mr. Adivishnu Reddy
doesn't meet Vimla's children today.

753
00:41:32.958 --> 00:41:34.833
they'll all leave.

754
00:41:35.958 --> 00:41:39.875
If you could pretend for a few days...

755
00:41:42.083 --> 00:41:43.083
Sorry. ma'am.

756
00:41:43.750 --> 00:41:45.208
I can't do this.

757
00:41:46.125 --> 00:41:50.792
These 15 days are all I get a year

758
00:41:51.292 --> 00:41:54.500
when I come to Shimla for some "me time".

759
00:41:55.958 --> 00:41:57.333
I don't want to ruin them.

760
00:41:57.625 --> 00:41:59.583
And honestly.

761
00:42:00.292 --> 00:42:01.750
I don't feel comfortable lying.

762
00:42:02.250 --> 00:42:03.792
I hate lies.

763
00:42:03.875 --> 00:42:05.042
I'm really sorry.

764
00:42:19.583 --> 00:42:20.625
Excuse me.

765
00:42:26.292 --> 00:42:27.417
Mr. Theeran...

766
00:42:28.667 --> 00:42:30.208
I hate lies too.

767
00:42:30.875 --> 00:42:31.958
But not more

768
00:42:32.250 --> 00:42:34.042
than I love my children.

769
00:42:34.917 --> 00:42:39.458
At least you get some "me time".

770
00:42:40.125 --> 00:42:44.750
I spend the whole year alone.

771
00:42:46.292 --> 00:42:48.917
I have a lot of "me time"

772
00:42:49.625 --> 00:42:53.125
but no "mom time".

773
00:42:53.833 --> 00:42:55.750
I am a mother after all.

774
00:42:55.833 --> 00:42:57.375
So yes. I got selfish.

775
00:42:57.917 --> 00:42:58.917
And I lied.

776
00:43:01.167 --> 00:43:03.625
Anyway… thank you.

777
00:43:18.125 --> 00:43:19.625
- Fateh.
- Yes. sir.

778
00:43:19.708 --> 00:43:21.750
- Prepare food for Mr. Reddy.
- Yes.

779
00:43:21.833 --> 00:43:23.625
And pack some clothes.

780
00:43:23.708 --> 00:43:24.875
Okay.

781
00:43:25.792 --> 00:43:27.875
- I'll get it. You carry on.
- Thanks.

782
00:43:37.083 --> 00:43:38.583
Yes? Can I help you?

783
00:43:42.042 --> 00:43:43.292
Captain Adivishnu Reddy?

784
00:43:43.792 --> 00:43:45.875
- I...
- Have you no shame?

785
00:43:46.208 --> 00:43:51.917
At this age. you should be retiring.
not romancing our mother.

786
00:43:52.500 --> 00:43:53.500
Who are you?

787
00:43:53.792 --> 00:43:55.125
We are Vimla Ahuja's children.

788
00:43:55.208 --> 00:43:58.083
the one you're fooling.
thinking she is alone.

789
00:43:58.167 --> 00:43:59.167
You've got it all wrong.

790
00:43:59.208 --> 00:44:00.625
We've got it wrong?

791
00:44:00.958 --> 00:44:02.500
No. what you're doing is wrong.

792
00:44:02.917 --> 00:44:05.208
This will bring disgrace.

793
00:44:06.542 --> 00:44:10.375
We have a reputation. a social standing.

794
00:44:10.458 --> 00:44:12.583
Everything will be ruined.

795
00:44:12.667 --> 00:44:13.875
Listen. Captain.

796
00:44:13.958 --> 00:44:16.083
Don't come to our house tonight.

797
00:44:16.167 --> 00:44:18.125
End this madness.

798
00:44:18.208 --> 00:44:21.375
Leave our mother alone and walk away.

799
00:44:21.833 --> 00:44:23.792
So we can go back.

800
00:44:23.875 --> 00:44:25.958
We have businesses worth crores on hold.

801
00:44:26.042 --> 00:44:28.750
If I see you near my mother again...

802
00:44:28.833 --> 00:44:30.042
Wait. sir.

803
00:44:30.125 --> 00:44:31.292
Let me speak.

804
00:44:33.875 --> 00:44:34.875
Listen. Captain.

805
00:44:36.125 --> 00:44:37.333
Stay away from their family.

806
00:44:38.125 --> 00:44:40.208
Because now their family

807
00:44:41.250 --> 00:44:42.500
is protected by Tony Kalra.

808
00:44:42.583 --> 00:44:43.667
Tony Kalra who?

809
00:44:45.250 --> 00:44:47.167
Me. Myself. Tony Kalra.

810
00:44:48.458 --> 00:44:54.167
Tony Kalra won't stand it if someone
snatches a toy from a Kalra kid.

811
00:44:54.667 --> 00:44:57.625
And you're trying
to take away their mother.

812
00:45:00.792 --> 00:45:02.083
Think about the consequences.

813
00:45:03.375 --> 00:45:05.016
You'll be running for your life. Captain.

814
00:45:05.750 --> 00:45:08.083
And running in the hills isn't easy.

815
00:45:08.500 --> 00:45:09.958
Roads have ups and down.

816
00:45:10.042 --> 00:45:11.202
you'll be gasping for breath.

817
00:45:12.167 --> 00:45:13.250
Do you understand?

818
00:45:13.917 --> 00:45:15.542
I hope you understood.

819
00:45:15.625 --> 00:45:17.042
I made a mistake.

820
00:45:17.750 --> 00:45:19.000
I completely understood.

821
00:45:20.292 --> 00:45:22.708
- Thank you.
- Bye.

822
00:45:22.917 --> 00:45:23.917
Thank you. sir.

823
00:45:24.458 --> 00:45:26.458
Nice. old boy.

824
00:45:27.792 --> 00:45:28.875
Let's go.

825
00:45:36.625 --> 00:45:39.042
- Did you see my temper?
- Let's go.

826
00:45:44.167 --> 00:45:45.583
- Sir.
- Yes?

827
00:45:45.667 --> 00:45:48.208
- Good thing he got scared easily.
- Right.

828
00:45:48.292 --> 00:45:51.542
I was feeling slightly awkward
because of his age.

829
00:45:51.625 --> 00:45:54.375
No. you were right.
No need to feel awkward.

830
00:45:54.458 --> 00:45:56.292
You were spot on.

831
00:45:56.375 --> 00:45:58.958
In fact. if he hadn't agreed.

832
00:45:59.042 --> 00:46:01.917
I had some lines which I had rehearsed.

833
00:46:02.000 --> 00:46:04.000
- What lines?
- The lines were...

834
00:46:04.083 --> 00:46:06.167
"My name is Jeevan. which means life."

835
00:46:06.250 --> 00:46:12.250
"To save his family's honor.
Jeevan can give his life

836
00:46:12.333 --> 00:46:14.417
and also..."

837
00:46:15.250 --> 00:46:17.333
Take one!

838
00:46:18.500 --> 00:46:20.083
What a dialogue. Brother!

839
00:46:20.167 --> 00:46:22.417
- Congratulations!
- Why are you shouting?

840
00:46:22.500 --> 00:46:23.500
Sorry. guys.

841
00:46:23.583 --> 00:46:24.917
We won't need it anymore.

842
00:46:25.000 --> 00:46:26.542
No more.

843
00:46:26.625 --> 00:46:28.833
What next. sir? What do we do now?

844
00:46:28.917 --> 00:46:31.417
What will we do?
We leave for Delhi tomorrow.

845
00:46:31.500 --> 00:46:33.583
Engagement in the evening.

846
00:46:34.333 --> 00:46:36.167
Wedding in two days.

847
00:46:36.250 --> 00:46:37.875
But Kannu asked for two years.

848
00:46:37.958 --> 00:46:40.083
No waiting.

849
00:46:40.917 --> 00:46:43.750
I've found a perfect son-in-law.
I'm not waiting two years.

850
00:46:43.833 --> 00:46:44.833
Thank you. sir.

851
00:46:44.875 --> 00:46:46.125
Soon. Very soon.

852
00:46:46.208 --> 00:46:48.750
Love you. son.

853
00:46:48.833 --> 00:46:50.875
Tony... you're a gem.

854
00:46:50.958 --> 00:46:52.000
Come on.

855
00:46:52.125 --> 00:46:53.375
Cheers.

856
00:47:02.333 --> 00:47:04.375
We solved a big problem today.

857
00:47:04.458 --> 00:47:07.250
But remember one thing. Mr. Naag.

858
00:47:08.208 --> 00:47:11.375
Don't let Ms. Vimla know
we threatened Reddy.

859
00:47:12.083 --> 00:47:13.958
It gives off a sketchy vibe.

860
00:47:14.042 --> 00:47:16.000
Who will tell her?

861
00:47:16.083 --> 00:47:18.167
Only we know.

862
00:47:18.625 --> 00:47:20.667
And Reddy must be halfway

863
00:47:20.750 --> 00:47:22.875
to Kanpur by now.

864
00:47:23.375 --> 00:47:25.708
But Kanpur isn't
on the way to Chennai.

865
00:47:25.792 --> 00:47:27.042
Doesn't matter.

866
00:47:27.125 --> 00:47:29.792
At least he's out of our lives.

867
00:47:45.125 --> 00:47:47.917
Naag. Jeevan. Tony. Come.

868
00:47:50.250 --> 00:47:51.375
Careful.

869
00:47:53.583 --> 00:47:54.708
Where were you all?

870
00:47:57.000 --> 00:47:58.000
Let me introduce you.

871
00:47:58.042 --> 00:48:00.583
Captain Adivishnu Reddy.

872
00:48:01.083 --> 00:48:02.083
Hello. boys.

873
00:48:03.667 --> 00:48:05.292
We've met before.

874
00:48:06.583 --> 00:48:07.583
Where?

875
00:48:12.417 --> 00:48:16.208
In the last six months.
Vimla told me so much about her family.

876
00:48:16.292 --> 00:48:18.708
I feel like I know you all.

877
00:48:18.792 --> 00:48:21.500
But Mr. Tony met Grandma
just two days ago.

878
00:48:22.500 --> 00:48:23.958
But I know him.

879
00:48:24.042 --> 00:48:25.917
Kalra Sweets. 17 outlets.

880
00:48:26.000 --> 00:48:28.208
And his wedding got canceled
because of us.

881
00:48:35.208 --> 00:48:37.500
Have you fixed a wedding date?

882
00:48:38.667 --> 00:48:40.500
- The twenty-forth.
- The twenty-forth?

883
00:48:41.292 --> 00:48:42.625
That's four days away.

884
00:48:42.708 --> 00:48:44.125
Too soon?

885
00:48:44.792 --> 00:48:46.667
Four days is perfect for me.

886
00:48:48.125 --> 00:48:49.250
Don't worry. Grandpa.

887
00:48:49.333 --> 00:48:52.292
I'll handle everything.
Four days are more than enough.

888
00:48:53.000 --> 00:48:55.083
She needs two years
for her own wedding

889
00:48:55.500 --> 00:48:57.667
but four days are enough
to plan his wedding.

890
00:49:00.875 --> 00:49:02.000
Let's keep it simple.

891
00:49:02.375 --> 00:49:05.417
You all are here. that's enough.

892
00:49:05.500 --> 00:49:06.500
You're right.

893
00:49:06.625 --> 00:49:08.083
Enjoy your mom time.

894
00:49:08.167 --> 00:49:09.458
Call me if needed.

895
00:49:09.542 --> 00:49:11.083
- I'm just a call away.
- Thank you.

896
00:49:11.167 --> 00:49:12.247
Okay. I'll take your leave.

897
00:49:12.375 --> 00:49:14.875
- I'll see you out...
- No. stay seated. ma'am.

898
00:49:15.792 --> 00:49:17.083
We'll see him off.

899
00:49:17.167 --> 00:49:18.542
- Please come. sir.
- Okay.

900
00:49:18.625 --> 00:49:20.042
- Bye.
- Bye.

901
00:49:20.125 --> 00:49:21.125
Bye.

902
00:49:21.292 --> 00:49:22.625
- Bye. Grandpa.
- Bye.

903
00:49:23.500 --> 00:49:24.792
<i>Welcome. sir.</i>

904
00:49:25.083 --> 00:49:26.375
<i>The guest is God.</i>

905
00:49:40.208 --> 00:49:42.292
I forgot to tell you something.

906
00:49:43.208 --> 00:49:44.333
I'll say it now.

907
00:49:45.000 --> 00:49:46.750
Listen to it carefully.

908
00:49:47.875 --> 00:49:50.250
My name is Jeevan...

909
00:49:50.792 --> 00:49:54.792
And for my family's honor...

910
00:49:56.750 --> 00:49:57.750
What was it?

911
00:49:58.167 --> 00:50:00.125
"I can give my life and take one too."

912
00:50:00.208 --> 00:50:01.250
Yes.

913
00:50:01.458 --> 00:50:03.750
I can give my life.

914
00:50:04.500 --> 00:50:06.667
and give my life...

915
00:50:06.750 --> 00:50:07.667
No. wrong.

916
00:50:07.750 --> 00:50:08.917
Take a life.

917
00:50:09.000 --> 00:50:09.917
Yes.

918
00:50:10.000 --> 00:50:12.083
I can give my life

919
00:50:12.958 --> 00:50:16.625
and also take a life.

920
00:50:17.333 --> 00:50:19.125
My name is Naag.

921
00:50:19.208 --> 00:50:21.708
When I strike.
people don't even ask for water.

922
00:50:21.792 --> 00:50:22.917
Then what do they ask for?

923
00:50:23.000 --> 00:50:25.000
Hello. Constable.

924
00:50:25.083 --> 00:50:27.042
Don't joke about him.

925
00:50:27.125 --> 00:50:28.792
You've retired from the army.

926
00:50:28.875 --> 00:50:30.250
not from romance.

927
00:50:30.333 --> 00:50:31.458
Tom Cruise.

928
00:50:32.792 --> 00:50:34.375
We also have grandparents at home.

929
00:50:35.042 --> 00:50:37.208
But they don't behave like this.

930
00:50:38.042 --> 00:50:39.333
You're from Delhi?

931
00:50:39.417 --> 00:50:40.417
Yes.

932
00:50:41.083 --> 00:50:43.583
Our blood doesn't flow.

933
00:50:44.458 --> 00:50:46.542
it storms through our veins.

934
00:50:47.292 --> 00:50:50.667
And Delhi people explain
in two ways.

935
00:50:52.000 --> 00:50:53.000
First.

936
00:50:53.500 --> 00:50:54.500
politely.

937
00:50:55.292 --> 00:50:56.833
Like I explained in the morning.

938
00:50:56.917 --> 00:50:57.917
What's the second?

939
00:50:57.958 --> 00:50:59.042
Secondly...

940
00:51:00.333 --> 00:51:01.625
Violence.

941
00:51:02.250 --> 00:51:03.292
Naag.

942
00:51:43.750 --> 00:51:44.875
Mommy!

943
00:51:44.958 --> 00:51:47.167
Mommy! Mommy...

944
00:51:47.250 --> 00:51:48.250
Brother...

945
00:51:56.250 --> 00:51:57.458
Have a good day. sir.

946
00:52:00.125 --> 00:52:02.000
Sir...

947
00:52:02.083 --> 00:52:03.250
Sir

948
00:52:03.542 --> 00:52:05.375
the main party has left.

949
00:52:05.667 --> 00:52:07.000
No issue between us.

950
00:52:08.458 --> 00:52:10.875
You're the son-in-law
of this family. so am I.

951
00:52:11.125 --> 00:52:12.625
Let's have a drink.

952
00:52:13.333 --> 00:52:14.333
Just a little...

953
00:52:14.375 --> 00:52:16.208
It's in the trunk. Not too far.

954
00:52:19.125 --> 00:52:20.417
Look. Tony Kalra.

955
00:52:21.292 --> 00:52:23.042
don't anger me again.

956
00:52:23.458 --> 00:52:25.708
My eyes see as much red

957
00:52:26.500 --> 00:52:28.708
as the one pumps through your veins.

958
00:52:28.792 --> 00:52:29.958
Yes. Major.

959
00:52:30.375 --> 00:52:31.750
And remember.

960
00:52:32.083 --> 00:52:34.167
You're from Delhi.

961
00:52:34.250 --> 00:52:36.333
but I belong to all of India.

962
00:52:49.333 --> 00:52:50.583
Goodnight. General.

963
00:53:00.000 --> 00:53:01.833
Kannu. once the candles are set.

964
00:53:01.917 --> 00:53:03.333
it'll look beautiful.

965
00:53:03.417 --> 00:53:06.958
I have a question...
why haven't you left yet?

966
00:53:07.042 --> 00:53:10.875
Your grandpa said he would feel bad
if I didn't attend the wedding.

967
00:53:10.958 --> 00:53:12.958
So I stayed back.

968
00:53:13.042 --> 00:53:15.083
What do you think about
my future grandpa?

969
00:53:15.167 --> 00:53:16.750
He's amazing.

970
00:53:16.833 --> 00:53:20.292
Last night. he put his hand
on my shoulder and said.

971
00:53:20.375 --> 00:53:22.917
"Love doesn't run in veins.

972
00:53:23.000 --> 00:53:25.042
it shines through the eyes."

973
00:53:25.125 --> 00:53:26.958
What a romantic gentleman he is!

974
00:53:27.042 --> 00:53:29.750
He even said.
"You're the son-in-law. so am I."

975
00:53:29.833 --> 00:53:32.333
Wanted to drink together.
but I said I didn't drink.

976
00:53:33.208 --> 00:53:34.708
You couldn't even stand last night.

977
00:53:34.792 --> 00:53:35.792
Was that lime water?

978
00:53:35.833 --> 00:53:37.042
"I don't drink."

979
00:53:37.125 --> 00:53:38.458
Happy...

980
00:53:38.542 --> 00:53:40.625
Get four more candles.

981
00:53:46.292 --> 00:53:47.292
What do you want?

982
00:53:47.333 --> 00:53:48.625
What are you doing. Tony?

983
00:53:48.708 --> 00:53:50.583
Something I should've done earlier.

984
00:53:50.667 --> 00:53:51.792
Jeevan?

985
00:53:52.083 --> 00:53:53.083
Look. Tony.

986
00:53:53.167 --> 00:53:55.208
We need each other right now.

987
00:53:55.292 --> 00:53:56.750
I needed you too

988
00:53:56.833 --> 00:53:58.083
when you ran away last night.

989
00:53:58.167 --> 00:53:59.167
Did you think then?

990
00:53:59.250 --> 00:54:01.167
They did. that's why they ran.

991
00:54:01.250 --> 00:54:03.125
Baby. leave it.

992
00:54:03.208 --> 00:54:05.250
Tony. forgive us.

993
00:54:05.333 --> 00:54:08.000
Please don't be upset.

994
00:54:08.083 --> 00:54:08.917
Here.

995
00:54:09.000 --> 00:54:10.750
grandma's wedding schedule.

996
00:54:10.833 --> 00:54:12.875
Sister Kannu sent it for review.

997
00:54:12.958 --> 00:54:15.667
Did you raise him just
to deliver bad news?

998
00:54:16.208 --> 00:54:18.208
Here... your mother's wedding schedule.

999
00:54:18.292 --> 00:54:20.375
Check it properly.
Don't miss out on any event.

1000
00:54:22.500 --> 00:54:26.208
We welcome you to the wedding
of Ms. Vimla Ahuja.

1001
00:54:26.375 --> 00:54:29.208
resident of Anand Cottage. Mashobra.

1002
00:54:29.333 --> 00:54:31.583
with Captain Adivishnu Reddy.

1003
00:54:31.667 --> 00:54:34.167
resident of Kala-Kavita Kunj. Sanjauli.

1004
00:54:34.417 --> 00:54:36.667
- Here is the...
- Wait. ma'am.

1005
00:54:39.833 --> 00:54:40.875
Take it.

1006
00:54:41.083 --> 00:54:42.417
I'll be back.

1007
00:54:42.500 --> 00:54:43.500
Hey...

1008
00:54:45.708 --> 00:54:47.958
Why did he run away after seeing the iPad?

1009
00:54:48.042 --> 00:54:50.292
Why do you keep bringing this
in front of everyone?

1010
00:55:16.250 --> 00:55:17.250
Where is Tony?

1011
00:55:17.292 --> 00:55:19.375
He's not even answering his phone.

1012
00:55:20.542 --> 00:55:22.226
- What did he see on the iPad?
- I don't know.

1013
00:55:22.250 --> 00:55:24.125
Wow.

1014
00:55:24.208 --> 00:55:27.208
The house looks beautiful
after so long.

1015
00:55:27.292 --> 00:55:28.542
When was the last time?

1016
00:55:28.708 --> 00:55:30.708
Twenty years ago.
At Naagendra's wedding.

1017
00:55:30.792 --> 00:55:33.083
Did you do all this. Kannu?

1018
00:55:33.583 --> 00:55:35.750
Tony helped me.

1019
00:55:35.833 --> 00:55:37.583
But where is Tony?

1020
00:55:37.667 --> 00:55:39.292
He must be around here somewhere.

1021
00:55:39.875 --> 00:55:42.167
I don't see him.

1022
00:55:43.583 --> 00:55:44.458
Good evening.

1023
00:55:44.542 --> 00:55:46.042
Where are you coming from. Tony?

1024
00:55:46.125 --> 00:55:49.583
Ma'am. I went to bring
a special guest.

1025
00:55:50.208 --> 00:55:51.417
Come. madam.

1026
00:56:02.042 --> 00:56:03.125
Let me introduce you

1027
00:56:03.458 --> 00:56:05.708
this is Mrs. Kavita Reddy.

1028
00:56:05.792 --> 00:56:08.417
Captain Adivishnu Reddy's second wife.

1029
00:56:09.042 --> 00:56:10.167
Second wife?

1030
00:56:11.625 --> 00:56:15.042
Yes. His first wife was
Mrs. Kalavathi Reddy.

1031
00:56:15.542 --> 00:56:18.792
After her demise. he remarried to her

1032
00:56:18.875 --> 00:56:21.958
and renamed his house
from Kala Kunj to Kala-Kavita Kunj.

1033
00:56:22.375 --> 00:56:24.208
What are you trying to say. Tony?

1034
00:56:24.292 --> 00:56:26.375
I'm saying
the Captain is fooling us.

1035
00:56:26.750 --> 00:56:30.167
Without divorcing Ms. Kavita.
he's marrying our grandma a second time...

1036
00:56:30.250 --> 00:56:32.167
Sorry. make that the third time.

1037
00:56:32.250 --> 00:56:34.333
But how can he do something like that?

1038
00:56:34.750 --> 00:56:36.833
Reddy can do anything.

1039
00:56:40.458 --> 00:56:43.958
He's always chasing other women
instead of being with his wife.

1040
00:56:44.500 --> 00:56:46.667
More active on dating apps
than at home.

1041
00:56:48.208 --> 00:56:50.292
Goes to Bangkok.
saying he's going to Bengaluru.

1042
00:56:50.708 --> 00:56:55.000
I've even seen him flirting
with mannequins at sari stores.

1043
00:56:57.250 --> 00:56:59.208
He's already ruined my life.

1044
00:56:59.292 --> 00:57:02.792
I won't let him ruin another.

1045
00:57:04.750 --> 00:57:06.833
I won't spare him.

1046
00:57:07.542 --> 00:57:08.542
See you.

1047
00:57:08.667 --> 00:57:09.667
Thank you. ma'am.

1048
00:57:21.833 --> 00:57:23.917
Grandma. Grandpa is here.

1049
00:57:24.708 --> 00:57:26.125
I mean that man is here.

1050
00:57:34.750 --> 00:57:35.750
Good evening. everyone.

1051
00:57:37.458 --> 00:57:40.542
Looks like you were waiting for me.

1052
00:57:40.625 --> 00:57:45.042
To tell you your truth is out.

1053
00:57:45.417 --> 00:57:46.417
What do you mean?

1054
00:57:46.500 --> 00:57:49.042
Your wife was here.

1055
00:57:49.125 --> 00:57:50.000
Which wife?

1056
00:57:50.083 --> 00:57:52.792
He has so many wives.
he doesn't even know

1057
00:57:52.875 --> 00:57:54.208
which one came.

1058
00:57:54.292 --> 00:57:57.250
Did you name your house
after your neighbors?

1059
00:58:00.250 --> 00:58:03.250
You almost trapped our mother-in-law.

1060
00:58:04.042 --> 00:58:05.125
Thanks to Tony.

1061
00:58:05.792 --> 00:58:08.917
who saved our reputation
from getting maligned.

1062
00:58:09.250 --> 00:58:13.083
I swear. if it weren't for your age...

1063
00:58:13.167 --> 00:58:14.958
Naag. stop.

1064
00:58:15.042 --> 00:58:16.082
Don't say anything to him.

1065
00:58:16.417 --> 00:58:18.000
- You don't know...
- Vimla.

1066
00:58:18.417 --> 00:58:19.458
Let them speak.

1067
00:58:19.542 --> 00:58:21.417
There's nothing left to say. Mr. Reddy.

1068
00:58:21.500 --> 00:58:22.958
Before I call the police.

1069
00:58:23.042 --> 00:58:24.417
please leave.

1070
00:58:26.667 --> 00:58:27.750
Please leave.

1071
00:58:34.625 --> 00:58:36.167
Everyone. let's go inside. Come on.

1072
00:58:36.333 --> 00:58:37.375
- Captain.
- Let's go.

1073
00:58:38.000 --> 00:58:39.042
Mom. you too.

1074
00:58:39.167 --> 00:58:40.458
Please come inside.

1075
00:58:43.375 --> 00:58:44.750
Do you know. Captain

1076
00:58:44.833 --> 00:58:47.792
my grandma passed away
more than 25 years ago.

1077
00:58:47.875 --> 00:58:50.625
But whenever my grandpa
looks at her photo.

1078
00:58:50.708 --> 00:58:53.458
it feels like she's still there.

1079
00:58:54.042 --> 00:58:55.292
Still around.

1080
00:58:55.875 --> 00:58:58.417
And your wife lives
just two kilometers away

1081
00:58:58.750 --> 00:58:59.958
and you...

1082
00:59:00.958 --> 00:59:04.333
Shame on you. Captain.

1083
00:59:09.000 --> 00:59:10.500
I'm sorry. Mr. Theeran.

1084
00:59:10.583 --> 00:59:12.708
You had to go through
so much because of me.

1085
00:59:12.792 --> 00:59:13.917
<i>No. no. Ms. Vimla.</i>

1086
00:59:14.000 --> 00:59:15.583
<i>It's my fault too.</i>

1087
00:59:16.458 --> 00:59:19.792
I should've thought
about the complications

1088
00:59:20.875 --> 00:59:23.542
that come with the name Adivishnu.

1089
00:59:24.167 --> 00:59:26.601
But wouldn't it have been better
if I had told everyone the truth?

1090
00:59:26.625 --> 00:59:28.792
<i>You will tell the truth.</i>

1091
00:59:28.875 --> 00:59:31.083
but this isn't the right time.

1092
00:59:32.042 --> 00:59:34.375
Your four days of "mom time"
aren't over yet.

1093
00:59:35.250 --> 00:59:37.750
Let's make the children stay
for two more days.

1094
00:59:38.708 --> 00:59:39.917
And if anyone wants to leave.

1095
00:59:40.833 --> 00:59:42.917
we'll let them go.

1096
00:59:49.667 --> 00:59:51.792
Careful. son. Careful.

1097
00:59:52.625 --> 00:59:54.708
Bobby.

1098
00:59:56.083 --> 00:59:58.167
Come. Kannu. Let me carry that.

1099
00:59:59.417 --> 01:00:00.958
- Thanks.
- You're welcome.

1100
01:00:01.125 --> 01:00:02.500
Not for the bags.

1101
01:00:02.583 --> 01:00:04.167
It's for saving my grandma.

1102
01:00:04.292 --> 01:00:06.292
It's okay. Kannu ji.
We're family after all.

1103
01:00:06.917 --> 01:00:07.917
You're right. Tony.

1104
01:00:08.667 --> 01:00:10.292
It was always about family.

1105
01:00:13.500 --> 01:00:15.500
I'm really sorry
about what happened last night.

1106
01:00:17.708 --> 01:00:19.792
It's okay. What's done is done.

1107
01:00:20.125 --> 01:00:22.208
At least we got
to meet you. Mother-in-law.

1108
01:00:22.833 --> 01:00:23.917
Come along.

1109
01:00:24.125 --> 01:00:26.000
Yes. ma'am. The engagement is on Sunday.

1110
01:00:26.125 --> 01:00:27.292
You should come.

1111
01:00:28.167 --> 01:00:32.375
Are you sure you'll get engaged?

1112
01:00:42.667 --> 01:00:45.583
Which of you is Mr. Tony Kalra?

1113
01:00:49.292 --> 01:00:51.250
I am Tony Kalra.

1114
01:00:51.333 --> 01:00:52.542
You are under arrest.

1115
01:00:52.625 --> 01:00:54.708
But... what did I do?

1116
01:00:57.625 --> 01:01:01.417
Mr. Tony tried to defame me

1117
01:01:01.750 --> 01:01:03.833
in front of my future family.

1118
01:01:04.208 --> 01:01:09.625
And he hurt the sentiments
of my late wife. Kavita Reddy.

1119
01:01:09.708 --> 01:01:11.292
Late wife?

1120
01:01:11.375 --> 01:01:13.167
Then who was that woman yesterday?

1121
01:01:13.250 --> 01:01:15.333
That was her.

1122
01:01:16.667 --> 01:01:19.000
She is Kavita Reddy.

1123
01:01:19.875 --> 01:01:21.167
Tell them.

1124
01:01:21.250 --> 01:01:23.792
My name is not Kavita Reddy.

1125
01:01:24.708 --> 01:01:27.042
- It's Sunita Verman.
- What...

1126
01:01:27.125 --> 01:01:32.375
And Mr. Tony Kalra forced Sunita
to pretend to be Kavita

1127
01:01:32.458 --> 01:01:34.542
by bribing her
with one hundred thousand rupees.

1128
01:01:35.083 --> 01:01:36.393
I gave her one hundred thousand rupees?

1129
01:01:36.417 --> 01:01:37.667
Great.

1130
01:01:37.750 --> 01:01:39.333
Confession before arraignment.

1131
01:01:39.667 --> 01:01:40.667
Wise man.

1132
01:01:40.708 --> 01:01:42.625
Say something. Mr. Ahuja.
You know everything.

1133
01:01:42.708 --> 01:01:43.958
How would I know?

1134
01:01:44.042 --> 01:01:46.417
You told us the whole story.

1135
01:01:46.500 --> 01:01:48.750
We trusted you. Tony.

1136
01:01:49.125 --> 01:01:51.583
But you broke our trust by lying.

1137
01:01:51.667 --> 01:01:52.792
- No. ma'am...
- And yes.

1138
01:01:52.875 --> 01:01:56.083
No one leaves Shimla
without my permission.

1139
01:01:56.417 --> 01:01:57.292
Why us?

1140
01:01:57.375 --> 01:01:58.875
I may need your statements.

1141
01:02:00.417 --> 01:02:02.375
I haven't done anything. Mrs. Ahuja

1142
01:02:02.458 --> 01:02:04.167
this woman is lying.

1143
01:02:04.250 --> 01:02:05.476
- Come on. let's go.
- Why are you lying?

1144
01:02:05.500 --> 01:02:07.500
- Come on. Mr. Tony.
- You used to be Kavita Reddy.

1145
01:02:07.542 --> 01:02:09.458
- Tony. let's go.
- I haven't done anything.

1146
01:02:09.542 --> 01:02:10.542
Let's go.

1147
01:02:10.583 --> 01:02:11.458
- Mr. Ahuja.
- Move.

1148
01:02:11.542 --> 01:02:12.708
Tony Kalra...

1149
01:02:12.792 --> 01:02:14.333
Kannu. she's lying.

1150
01:02:16.167 --> 01:02:18.917
I never thought you'd stoop so low
for your own benefit.

1151
01:02:21.167 --> 01:02:22.208
You know what?

1152
01:02:22.750 --> 01:02:24.833
I never even wanted to marry you.

1153
01:02:25.208 --> 01:02:27.417
I only agreed
because my parents insisted.

1154
01:02:29.750 --> 01:02:30.875
Now just get lost.

1155
01:02:31.083 --> 01:02:33.167
And don't ever show me your face again.

1156
01:02:41.083 --> 01:02:42.167
- Let's go.
- Come on.

1157
01:02:42.250 --> 01:02:44.333
Come on.

1158
01:02:53.958 --> 01:02:55.684
- Don't just stand there. help us.
- Tony's luggage...

1159
01:02:55.708 --> 01:02:56.917
Leave it.

1160
01:02:57.000 --> 01:02:58.042
Give us a hand.

1161
01:03:52.958 --> 01:03:55.042
- Sunaina.
- Mom.

1162
01:03:56.542 --> 01:03:57.583
Sunaina

1163
01:03:59.833 --> 01:04:00.833
my child.

1164
01:04:01.375 --> 01:04:03.542
- Mom. why were the police here?
- Leave it.

1165
01:04:03.625 --> 01:04:04.792
Avni...

1166
01:04:04.875 --> 01:04:06.792
- You've grown up so much.
- Hello. Aunt.

1167
01:04:06.875 --> 01:04:08.458
Hello. Aunt.

1168
01:04:10.125 --> 01:04:12.958
- This is Bobby and Bittu.
- Hello.

1169
01:04:13.083 --> 01:04:13.917
- Hello.
- Hello.

1170
01:04:14.042 --> 01:04:15.333
Let's go inside.

1171
01:04:15.417 --> 01:04:17.792
These are your older and younger uncles.

1172
01:04:17.875 --> 01:04:19.417
and these are your aunts.

1173
01:04:19.583 --> 01:04:20.792
- Hi.
- Hi.

1174
01:04:21.083 --> 01:04:22.958
Her smile is just like her grandma.

1175
01:04:23.042 --> 01:04:25.125
Come on. let's go inside.

1176
01:04:27.708 --> 01:04:28.750
How are you. Brother?

1177
01:04:28.833 --> 01:04:30.250
We're good.

1178
01:04:30.750 --> 01:04:32.167
- How are you. Sunaina?
- I'm good.

1179
01:04:34.000 --> 01:04:36.958
- Looking lovely.
- Thank you.

1180
01:04:37.042 --> 01:04:39.833
Singapore really suits you.

1181
01:04:39.917 --> 01:04:41.875
Aunt Sunaina...

1182
01:04:41.958 --> 01:04:43.458
How are you. Kannu?

1183
01:04:43.583 --> 01:04:45.708
I'm very good. How are you?

1184
01:04:46.875 --> 01:04:49.500
Come inside. Come fast.

1185
01:04:49.833 --> 01:04:52.125
Here comes Mom's real daughter.

1186
01:04:53.542 --> 01:04:55.625
Now she'll do exactly

1187
01:04:56.542 --> 01:04:58.000
what we don't want.

1188
01:04:58.083 --> 01:05:00.042
At least whatever she does

1189
01:05:00.125 --> 01:05:01.583
will be her own choice.

1190
01:05:07.833 --> 01:05:09.917
What about Tony. Brother?

1191
01:05:11.500 --> 01:05:12.625
Forget about Tony.

1192
01:05:13.542 --> 01:05:15.625
Let's deal with her first.

1193
01:05:16.875 --> 01:05:18.625
So. Mr. Kalra...

1194
01:05:18.708 --> 01:05:20.792
Write. "Lying is a sin."

1195
01:05:21.583 --> 01:05:22.708
A thousand times.

1196
01:05:22.792 --> 01:05:24.417
I didn't lie. sir.

1197
01:05:24.500 --> 01:05:25.667
Five thousand times.

1198
01:05:25.750 --> 01:05:27.833
Sir. that lady claimed...

1199
01:05:28.917 --> 01:05:31.000
Ten thousand times.

1200
01:05:32.208 --> 01:05:34.292
Anything else?

1201
01:05:34.833 --> 01:05:36.250
Can I get a pen?

1202
01:05:36.333 --> 01:05:37.208
Pen.

1203
01:05:37.292 --> 01:05:38.292
Here you go. sir.

1204
01:05:51.792 --> 01:05:53.542
He'll never change.

1205
01:05:53.625 --> 01:05:55.458
And if I divorce him.

1206
01:05:55.542 --> 01:05:57.625
he'll ruin someone else's life.

1207
01:05:59.083 --> 01:06:00.917
You see. Mr. Theeran.

1208
01:06:01.000 --> 01:06:03.875
not every story has a happy ending.

1209
01:06:03.958 --> 01:06:05.875
But with what you're doing.

1210
01:06:05.958 --> 01:06:09.375
I'm sure this one will have one.

1211
01:06:09.750 --> 01:06:11.167
Of course. Ms. Kavita.

1212
01:06:11.250 --> 01:06:14.083
After all. Colonel sir
is handling everything.

1213
01:06:14.750 --> 01:06:15.917
Everything will be fine.

1214
01:06:16.000 --> 01:06:17.917
That's the problem.

1215
01:06:18.000 --> 01:06:22.208
These days. relationships
are treated like situations.

1216
01:06:22.292 --> 01:06:23.750
We use our brains

1217
01:06:23.833 --> 01:06:25.917
where we should use our hearts.

1218
01:06:26.292 --> 01:06:28.375
Tony is a bit cocky

1219
01:06:29.083 --> 01:06:31.292
but he's not a bad person.

1220
01:06:31.375 --> 01:06:32.708
Let him go soon.

1221
01:06:32.792 --> 01:06:35.333
That depends on his writing speed. sir.

1222
01:06:37.458 --> 01:06:38.667
So...

1223
01:06:39.667 --> 01:06:41.500
Okay. Thank you.

1224
01:06:41.625 --> 01:06:43.208
- Come. Ms. Kavita.
- Thanks. Mr. Azad.

1225
01:07:02.917 --> 01:07:04.250
Vimla.

1226
01:07:04.333 --> 01:07:06.333
your whole family
is here together today.

1227
01:07:06.458 --> 01:07:10.000
Credit goes to you. Reddy ji.
I'm so happy.

1228
01:07:10.083 --> 01:07:12.583
I can see that
from the glow on your face.

1229
01:07:12.667 --> 01:07:16.208
Grandpa... that glow is because of you.

1230
01:07:16.292 --> 01:07:18.375
Quiet. you naughty.

1231
01:07:19.458 --> 01:07:20.583
Look. Mr. Reddy...

1232
01:07:20.667 --> 01:07:22.417
I can't speak for everyone. But...

1233
01:07:23.000 --> 01:07:25.000
I hope Mom
has chosen the right person.

1234
01:07:25.458 --> 01:07:27.542
I'm happy for you. guys.

1235
01:07:27.792 --> 01:07:31.458
But to avoid any complications
after marriage...

1236
01:07:32.500 --> 01:07:36.208
So.
I'd want you to sign these papers.

1237
01:07:37.083 --> 01:07:38.125
What is this?

1238
01:07:38.208 --> 01:07:40.292
These are the property deeds. Mom.

1239
01:07:40.917 --> 01:07:44.417
The property in your name
is worth 80 million rupees.

1240
01:07:44.917 --> 01:07:48.208
The property is split equally
between you and us kids.

1241
01:07:48.292 --> 01:07:50.667
So each of us gets 20 million rupees.

1242
01:07:52.292 --> 01:07:54.708
I want my share now.

1243
01:07:55.625 --> 01:07:57.708
Otherwise. later

1244
01:07:58.542 --> 01:08:00.083
things might get complicated.

1245
01:08:00.167 --> 01:08:01.750
I knew it.

1246
01:08:01.833 --> 01:08:03.601
She wouldn't come to
Shimla without an agenda.

1247
01:08:03.625 --> 01:08:05.417
What agenda. Jeevan?

1248
01:08:05.500 --> 01:08:07.500
She's not saying anything wrong.

1249
01:08:07.583 --> 01:08:09.667
She's talking about her rights.

1250
01:08:10.500 --> 01:08:11.583
Yes. Mr. Reddy.

1251
01:08:11.792 --> 01:08:14.208
People may say anything.
but I've done my duty.

1252
01:08:14.292 --> 01:08:16.375
So I've come to claim my rights.

1253
01:08:16.458 --> 01:08:18.333
What duties are you talking about?

1254
01:08:18.417 --> 01:08:20.292
Last year. for the apple farm infestation.

1255
01:08:20.375 --> 01:08:22.625
I sent 1.2 million rupees for pesticides.

1256
01:08:22.708 --> 01:08:24.309
I send 20.000 rupees every month to Mom.

1257
01:08:24.375 --> 01:08:25.417
Right. Mom?

1258
01:08:25.500 --> 01:08:27.083
That's 240.000 rupees a year.

1259
01:08:27.167 --> 01:08:29.875
- What are you...
- Quiet. Absolutely quiet.

1260
01:08:30.375 --> 01:08:31.375
The elders are talking.

1261
01:08:31.417 --> 01:08:32.750
Take the kids inside.

1262
01:08:32.833 --> 01:08:33.917
Do I need to say it twice?

1263
01:08:35.958 --> 01:08:36.958
Go.

1264
01:08:38.542 --> 01:08:41.125
Now... what were you saying about duties?

1265
01:08:41.875 --> 01:08:43.268
You're going to lecture us on duties?

1266
01:08:43.292 --> 01:08:45.167
Mom's health insurance.

1267
01:08:45.250 --> 01:08:47.417
medicines. house maintenance...
I handle everything.

1268
01:08:48.250 --> 01:08:51.000
I'm the eldest. and I've
never run away from my responsibilities.

1269
01:08:51.458 --> 01:08:53.542
But I never came asking
for my rights like you.

1270
01:08:54.917 --> 01:08:58.917
Last year. I organized
two big family rituals.

1271
01:08:59.333 --> 01:09:01.875
Cost me nearly 400.000 rupees.

1272
01:09:01.958 --> 01:09:05.292
I never even mentioned it to anyone.

1273
01:09:05.750 --> 01:09:07.125
Why are you telling me all this?

1274
01:09:07.208 --> 01:09:08.792
You're her sons. It's your duty.

1275
01:09:08.875 --> 01:09:10.726
Yes. it's our duty as sons.
but what did you do?

1276
01:09:10.750 --> 01:09:12.375
What's your duty?

1277
01:09:12.458 --> 01:09:14.542
You got married
and left home without telling anyone.

1278
01:09:14.958 --> 01:09:17.042
We were humiliated everywhere.

1279
01:09:17.458 --> 01:09:19.583
Mom pampered you too much. otherwise...

1280
01:09:20.667 --> 01:09:22.125
You didn't even think about her.

1281
01:09:22.208 --> 01:09:24.042
I did. Brother.

1282
01:09:24.125 --> 01:09:27.167
Two years ago.
when the back wall collapsed in the rain.

1283
01:09:27.250 --> 01:09:28.542
I sent 75.000 rupees.

1284
01:09:28.625 --> 01:09:30.417
So what? Mom went to <i>Mahakumbh</i>.

1285
01:09:30.500 --> 01:09:34.667
I sent 31.000 rupees for the tickets
and 51.000 for a donation.

1286
01:09:34.750 --> 01:09:35.792
Mahakumbh.

1287
01:09:35.875 --> 01:09:39.458
A few months ago.
Mom's old car broke down.

1288
01:09:39.542 --> 01:09:42.625
I got it repaired
so she wouldn't have to walk.

1289
01:09:42.708 --> 01:09:45.542
It cost around 38.700 rupees.

1290
01:09:46.792 --> 01:09:48.208
I never told anyone.

1291
01:09:48.292 --> 01:09:50.375
Mom was sick. She was hospitalized.

1292
01:09:51.292 --> 01:09:53.292
She needed weekly injections.

1293
01:09:53.375 --> 01:09:54.708
Each injection cost 5.000 rupees.

1294
01:09:54.792 --> 01:09:57.875
Five thousand rupees. Do you understand?

1295
01:09:57.958 --> 01:09:59.125
I had just got a job.

1296
01:09:59.208 --> 01:10:00.625
I didn't have money.

1297
01:10:00.708 --> 01:10:02.500
I took a loan.

1298
01:10:02.583 --> 01:10:04.542
and repaid it for three years.

1299
01:10:04.625 --> 01:10:06.025
Three years. Do you even know that?

1300
01:10:06.083 --> 01:10:07.875
Jeevan. please...

1301
01:10:07.958 --> 01:10:09.458
Let's talk peacefully.

1302
01:10:09.542 --> 01:10:11.542
Peacefully?

1303
01:10:11.625 --> 01:10:12.833
Then you should talk.

1304
01:10:12.917 --> 01:10:15.000
I'm the crazy one.
I don't know anything.

1305
01:10:15.083 --> 01:10:17.167
I'm always wrong.

1306
01:10:48.333 --> 01:10:50.792
I'm the crazy one. I'm always wrong.

1307
01:10:50.875 --> 01:10:52.417
- Jeevan...
- I am the stupid one.

1308
01:10:52.500 --> 01:10:54.226
- Listen to me...
- No one wants to listen to me.

1309
01:10:54.250 --> 01:10:55.250
- Jeevan...
- She's right.

1310
01:10:55.333 --> 01:10:56.833
Go ahead. do what she says.

1311
01:10:56.917 --> 01:10:59.000
- At least listen to me.
- Baby.

1312
01:11:00.000 --> 01:11:02.083
Baby!

1313
01:11:07.208 --> 01:11:09.917
See. this is what I meant
by complications.

1314
01:11:11.167 --> 01:11:13.833
Anyway. the papers are ready.

1315
01:11:13.917 --> 01:11:16.000
Please go through them.

1316
01:11:26.208 --> 01:11:28.167
I don't know what's happening

1317
01:11:28.250 --> 01:11:30.167
to relationships these days.

1318
01:11:30.250 --> 01:11:31.917
Not to all the relationships.

1319
01:11:32.000 --> 01:11:34.083
Just to blood ties.

1320
01:11:50.333 --> 01:11:51.750
Done. sir.

1321
01:11:51.833 --> 01:11:53.667
May I leave?

1322
01:11:53.833 --> 01:11:55.708
- Of course.
- Thank you.

1323
01:11:59.083 --> 01:12:00.250
By the way. sir

1324
01:12:00.333 --> 01:12:02.667
believe it or not.

1325
01:12:03.417 --> 01:12:05.125
it was Ms. Kavita who lied.

1326
01:12:05.208 --> 01:12:06.417
not me.

1327
01:12:06.500 --> 01:12:10.125
It doesn't matter whether you lied or not.

1328
01:12:10.208 --> 01:12:12.292
What matters is

1329
01:12:12.375 --> 01:12:16.250
whether that lie was told for yourself
or for your loved ones.

1330
01:12:18.083 --> 01:12:20.208
Great... this is delicious.

1331
01:12:21.375 --> 01:12:22.458
Really.

1332
01:12:24.958 --> 01:12:26.333
Tony is calling.

1333
01:12:28.375 --> 01:12:31.292
What's up. my prince? Where are you?

1334
01:12:31.833 --> 01:12:33.833
I'm fine. Grandpa.

1335
01:12:33.917 --> 01:12:36.000
I wanted to tell you something.

1336
01:12:36.833 --> 01:12:38.583
I lied to you

1337
01:12:38.667 --> 01:12:40.750
for selfish reasons.

1338
01:12:41.208 --> 01:12:42.292
What happened. dear?

1339
01:12:43.375 --> 01:12:46.292
I'm not in Vietnam. I'm in Shimla.

1340
01:12:47.792 --> 01:12:49.875
<i>Please find it in your heart
to forgive me. Grandpa.</i>

1341
01:12:50.667 --> 01:12:52.750
It won't happen again.

1342
01:12:54.833 --> 01:12:56.917
I'm coming home.

1343
01:14:19.208 --> 01:14:21.042
<i>I never imagined</i>

1344
01:14:21.125 --> 01:14:24.458
<i>I'd have to lie just to keep
my children with me</i>

1345
01:14:24.542 --> 01:14:26.833
<i>for a few more days.</i>

1346
01:14:26.917 --> 01:14:29.583
<i>This whole wedding story began</i>

1347
01:14:29.667 --> 01:14:31.917
<i>when I attended Himani's wedding.</i>

1348
01:14:32.458 --> 01:14:35.875
<i>My post was misunderstood...
First by Facelook.</i>

1349
01:14:36.333 --> 01:14:38.417
<i>then by all of you.</i>

1350
01:14:38.792 --> 01:14:40.125
<i>After so many years.</i>

1351
01:14:40.208 --> 01:14:42.750
<i>seeing all of you at my doorstep</i>

1352
01:14:42.833 --> 01:14:44.333
<i>I got emotional.</i>

1353
01:14:44.417 --> 01:14:48.750
<i>And I lied
just to spend a little more time with you.</i>

1354
01:14:51.833 --> 01:14:55.250
<i>But that lie taught me something...</i>

1355
01:14:56.042 --> 01:14:58.125
<i>A mother doesn't have desires</i>

1356
01:14:59.375 --> 01:15:01.458
<i>only duties.</i>

1357
01:15:01.875 --> 01:15:04.125
<i>She gives birth.</i>

1358
01:15:04.208 --> 01:15:06.292
<i>teaches her children to speak</i>

1359
01:15:06.875 --> 01:15:09.083
<i>teaches them to walk.</i>

1360
01:15:09.167 --> 01:15:14.500
<i>and then waits for them
when they walk too far away.</i>

1361
01:15:14.917 --> 01:15:18.750
<i>Even if that wait lasts forever.</i>

1362
01:15:18.833 --> 01:15:21.292
<i>a mother has no right to complain.</i>

1363
01:15:23.083 --> 01:15:27.500
<i>I wasted everyone's precious time
for my own selfish wish.</i>

1364
01:15:27.958 --> 01:15:33.250
<i>Please... find it in your hearts
to forgive your selfish mother.</i>

1365
01:17:00.375 --> 01:17:02.458
This letter wasn't meant for you. Tony.

1366
01:17:04.458 --> 01:17:06.542
This letter was meant also for me. ma'am.

1367
01:17:06.958 --> 01:17:09.958
Because. even if it wasn't intentional.

1368
01:17:10.333 --> 01:17:12.625
I lied to Grandpa and hurt him.

1369
01:17:13.708 --> 01:17:16.625
The only difference here is that
I lied for myself.

1370
01:17:17.250 --> 01:17:18.792
and you lied for your family.

1371
01:17:18.875 --> 01:17:22.042
Give me a chance to make things right
by helping you. ma'am.

1372
01:17:22.125 --> 01:17:24.208
What's the point?

1373
01:17:24.833 --> 01:17:26.292
It's all over.

1374
01:17:26.375 --> 01:17:28.542
But it's not the end. ma'am.

1375
01:17:28.625 --> 01:17:29.875
We'll take care of everything.

1376
01:17:29.958 --> 01:17:32.000
This is beyond taking care of.

1377
01:17:32.083 --> 01:17:34.167
Their feelings are dead.

1378
01:17:34.250 --> 01:17:36.500
Feelings never die. Ms. Vimla.

1379
01:17:36.583 --> 01:17:39.958
Sometimes they are overpowered by greed.

1380
01:17:40.042 --> 01:17:42.792
Vimla. your children have lost their way.

1381
01:17:43.167 --> 01:17:46.125
They'll understand if we guide
them back on the right path.

1382
01:17:46.500 --> 01:17:49.083
Give us two days. ma'am. Only two days.

1383
01:17:49.542 --> 01:17:51.333
What will change in two days?

1384
01:17:51.417 --> 01:17:54.167
In two days. night turns into day.

1385
01:17:54.625 --> 01:17:56.708
And what will you gain from all this?

1386
01:17:58.500 --> 01:18:04.000
If helping you lets me atone
for lying to Grandpa.

1387
01:18:04.375 --> 01:18:06.458
I'll be able to face him with pride.

1388
01:18:06.917 --> 01:18:08.833
Ms. Vimla.

1389
01:18:08.917 --> 01:18:13.167
You spent years hoping
your children would come back.

1390
01:18:14.042 --> 01:18:16.125
What's two days?

1391
01:18:21.042 --> 01:18:23.625
I wonder who jinxed our happy family.

1392
01:18:24.250 --> 01:18:25.333
I don't understand.

1393
01:18:25.417 --> 01:18:27.667
Everything was going smooth.
and suddenly this...

1394
01:18:27.750 --> 01:18:29.458
Let's perform a ritual. Brother.

1395
01:18:29.542 --> 01:18:31.417
The Mother Goddess
will set everything right.

1396
01:18:31.500 --> 01:18:34.708
Have some freshly brewed tea
from Mr. Sharma.

1397
01:18:34.792 --> 01:18:36.208
Enjoy <i>pakora</i> with tea.

1398
01:18:36.292 --> 01:18:37.375
Take it.

1399
01:18:38.375 --> 01:18:39.875
Jeevan

1400
01:18:39.958 --> 01:18:41.917
seeing you in Shimla after a long time.

1401
01:18:42.000 --> 01:18:43.875
Anything special?

1402
01:18:43.958 --> 01:18:46.125
- The wedding.
- Oh. great. Whose wedding?

1403
01:18:46.208 --> 01:18:47.208
His mom.

1404
01:18:47.292 --> 01:18:49.375
Mom?

1405
01:18:51.083 --> 01:18:54.500
- Mom's granddaughter.
- I see.

1406
01:18:54.583 --> 01:18:56.208
Our daughter. Kannu.

1407
01:18:56.292 --> 01:18:58.125
Excellent.

1408
01:18:58.208 --> 01:18:59.542
Where is the boy from?

1409
01:18:59.625 --> 01:19:02.792
- He's from places...
- Yeah.

1410
01:19:02.875 --> 01:19:05.292
He's from all over the country...
He's from the army.

1411
01:19:05.375 --> 01:19:06.375
So. he's a soldier.

1412
01:19:06.458 --> 01:19:08.750
Don't hesitate to tell me
if you need my help.

1413
01:19:08.833 --> 01:19:09.958
- Of course.
- Thanks.

1414
01:19:10.042 --> 01:19:11.375
Enjoy the tea.

1415
01:19:11.458 --> 01:19:12.792
Tony's in the army?

1416
01:19:12.875 --> 01:19:14.375
You never told me.

1417
01:19:14.458 --> 01:19:16.542
- Oh. God.
- Leave it. Baby.

1418
01:19:18.458 --> 01:19:21.042
Did we make a mistake
by not supporting Tony?

1419
01:19:21.125 --> 01:19:23.208
Let's forget Tony for a while.

1420
01:19:23.708 --> 01:19:25.792
We're stuck here because of him.

1421
01:19:26.250 --> 01:19:28.708
We'll find someone better
for Kannu. please.

1422
01:19:29.542 --> 01:19:30.542
Enjoy your pakora.

1423
01:19:35.250 --> 01:19:40.000
Ms. Vimla. did you always know
Kannu didn't want to marry me?

1424
01:19:40.083 --> 01:19:41.958
How would I know. son?

1425
01:19:42.042 --> 01:19:44.625
I found out the day you guys came here.

1426
01:19:44.708 --> 01:19:46.958
That's why I was trying to send you back.

1427
01:19:47.042 --> 01:19:48.792
so your time wouldn't go to waste.

1428
01:19:48.875 --> 01:19:52.375
Ms. Vimla. time spent in love
is never wasted.

1429
01:19:52.458 --> 01:19:53.458
Correct. Colonel.

1430
01:19:53.958 --> 01:19:57.458
Kannu is back in my life
which is nothing short of a miracle.

1431
01:19:58.083 --> 01:20:00.167
If God has sent her back.

1432
01:20:00.708 --> 01:20:02.833
He must have a plan.

1433
01:20:02.917 --> 01:20:05.042
How... long have you known Kannu?

1434
01:20:05.667 --> 01:20:09.042
Eight years four months...
and today's the seventh day.

1435
01:20:09.125 --> 01:20:10.792
- Social media?
- No. college.

1436
01:20:10.875 --> 01:20:12.958
- Medical student?
- Arts.

1437
01:20:13.542 --> 01:20:14.833
One-sided love.

1438
01:20:16.417 --> 01:20:18.000
I mean

1439
01:20:18.083 --> 01:20:19.875
even I have one-sided love.

1440
01:20:19.958 --> 01:20:20.833
Why?

1441
01:20:20.917 --> 01:20:22.583
Colonel. don't you love her?

1442
01:20:22.667 --> 01:20:25.583
- I'm talking about my children.
- I know.

1443
01:20:35.792 --> 01:20:38.500
Ma'am. please go inside.
I'll get the luggage.

1444
01:20:47.708 --> 01:20:49.750
What are you doing here?

1445
01:20:49.833 --> 01:20:51.314
Kannu. I know you don't like my face.

1446
01:20:52.167 --> 01:20:53.167
The thing is...

1447
01:20:53.583 --> 01:20:57.333
Now I'm a guest
of the one who owns this place.

1448
01:20:57.417 --> 01:21:00.333
So. whenever I come here.
you can turn your face around.

1449
01:21:00.542 --> 01:21:01.542
Problem solved.

1450
01:21:03.083 --> 01:21:04.083
Excuse me.

1451
01:21:11.375 --> 01:21:12.500
Mom...

1452
01:21:18.417 --> 01:21:19.417
Thank you.

1453
01:21:20.125 --> 01:21:21.458
Sorry. Mr. Reddy.

1454
01:21:21.583 --> 01:21:23.875
Last night.
dinner was ruined by those two.

1455
01:21:23.958 --> 01:21:25.458
Don't worry. Ms. Sunaina.

1456
01:21:25.542 --> 01:21:28.542
We'll have breakfast.
lunch and dinner in this house hereon.

1457
01:21:28.625 --> 01:21:30.417
and no one will ruin it.

1458
01:21:30.500 --> 01:21:32.792
- Who are you?
- Tony Kalra.

1459
01:21:33.792 --> 01:21:35.125
And whose luggage is this?

1460
01:21:35.208 --> 01:21:36.333
It belongs to the Captain.

1461
01:21:36.417 --> 01:21:37.542
He's going to stay here now.

1462
01:21:42.333 --> 01:21:43.250
Ms. Vimla.

1463
01:21:43.333 --> 01:21:44.792
where do I keep the luggage?

1464
01:21:44.875 --> 01:21:46.125
Keep it in Jeevan's room.

1465
01:21:46.208 --> 01:21:47.208
Why my room?

1466
01:21:48.458 --> 01:21:51.000
How can you give my room
to the Captain. Mom?

1467
01:21:51.083 --> 01:21:53.000
The entire place belongs to him now.

1468
01:21:53.083 --> 01:21:56.167
Mr. Reddy is practically family now.

1469
01:21:56.250 --> 01:21:58.500
What do you mean? So what?

1470
01:21:58.583 --> 01:21:59.958
If he's practically family.

1471
01:22:00.042 --> 01:22:02.250
then where am I going to stay. Mom?

1472
01:22:02.750 --> 01:22:04.708
You can move into the guest room.

1473
01:22:04.792 --> 01:22:07.958
I should move in the guest room
in my own house?

1474
01:22:08.042 --> 01:22:09.434
That makes me a guest in my own house.

1475
01:22:09.458 --> 01:22:11.750
You behave like a guest.

1476
01:22:12.375 --> 01:22:13.768
You came to Shimla after so many years.

1477
01:22:13.792 --> 01:22:15.792
I am not talking to you. Mr. Reddy.

1478
01:22:15.875 --> 01:22:17.716
I am talking to my mom.
Please don't interfere.

1479
01:22:17.750 --> 01:22:21.167
Mom. if you give my room to him.
then I... I...

1480
01:22:21.250 --> 01:22:23.208
Alright. fine. Don't get angry.

1481
01:22:23.292 --> 01:22:24.500
Go to your room.

1482
01:22:24.583 --> 01:22:25.583
Yes.

1483
01:22:25.667 --> 01:22:27.875
<i>You can go to my room.</i>

1484
01:22:28.208 --> 01:22:29.125
What?

1485
01:22:29.208 --> 01:22:31.042
<i>So can I take the bag
to the room. right?</i>

1486
01:22:31.125 --> 01:22:32.542
<i>Just like that.</i>

1487
01:22:32.625 --> 01:22:34.208
<i>I'm taking the bag.</i>

1488
01:22:34.292 --> 01:22:36.250
- Okay.
- Okay.

1489
01:22:36.458 --> 01:22:39.292
What are they talking about?
What language is this?

1490
01:22:41.375 --> 01:22:42.292
She is speaking Tamil.

1491
01:22:42.375 --> 01:22:43.875
When did she learn Tamil?

1492
01:22:43.958 --> 01:22:45.875
Love teaches you everything. sir.

1493
01:22:45.958 --> 01:22:47.458
But what are they saying?

1494
01:22:47.542 --> 01:22:49.958
She's just saying
that you will all leave soon

1495
01:22:50.042 --> 01:22:51.458
and he can stay in her room.

1496
01:22:51.542 --> 01:22:55.250
- An after-wedding arrangement.
- No. Absolutely not.

1497
01:22:56.667 --> 01:22:59.542
I'll move into the guest room.

1498
01:23:00.042 --> 01:23:01.167
You can stay in my room.

1499
01:23:01.250 --> 01:23:04.292
Romal. move the luggage to the guest room.

1500
01:23:04.375 --> 01:23:05.708
It's only for some time.

1501
01:23:11.667 --> 01:23:15.250
But why did Grandma
give him Uncle Jeevan's room?

1502
01:23:16.042 --> 01:23:17.375
So what if she did?

1503
01:23:17.458 --> 01:23:19.458
We don't come to Shimla anyway.

1504
01:23:19.542 --> 01:23:21.667
How is Tony related to me?

1505
01:23:21.750 --> 01:23:24.042
He isn't. he just seems odd to me.

1506
01:23:24.542 --> 01:23:26.059
He was supposed to be my brother-in-law.

1507
01:23:26.083 --> 01:23:28.458
but that didn't happen because
of grandma's wedding.

1508
01:23:28.542 --> 01:23:30.625
What is a brother-in-law?

1509
01:23:30.958 --> 01:23:34.375
A brother-in-law is a creature
who needs full-time attention.

1510
01:23:34.750 --> 01:23:36.875
otherwise he stresses everyone out.

1511
01:23:36.958 --> 01:23:39.167
And later this brother-in-law
becomes that uncle.

1512
01:23:39.250 --> 01:23:41.583
who only gets miffed at weddings.

1513
01:23:44.958 --> 01:23:46.875
Grandma. Did you bring Tony back?

1514
01:23:46.958 --> 01:23:49.292
You and your parents brought him here.

1515
01:23:49.375 --> 01:23:50.375
Please. Grandma.

1516
01:23:50.458 --> 01:23:52.542
You know he wants
to call off your wedding.

1517
01:23:52.958 --> 01:23:54.792
Even your parents want that.

1518
01:23:54.875 --> 01:23:56.500
but the only difference is

1519
01:23:56.583 --> 01:23:59.250
your parents are doing
it to save their face.

1520
01:23:59.583 --> 01:24:01.208
And Tony is doing it

1521
01:24:01.292 --> 01:24:02.667
for the sake of his love.

1522
01:24:03.458 --> 01:24:05.542
Anyway. you won't understand.

1523
01:24:16.292 --> 01:24:18.167
Tony. what are you doing?

1524
01:24:18.250 --> 01:24:20.101
It's pretty cold. ma'am.
Just getting some heat.

1525
01:24:20.125 --> 01:24:22.958
Romal asks. what are you doing. Tony?

1526
01:24:23.542 --> 01:24:26.000
You suddenly switched sides
to join Mom and the Captain.

1527
01:24:26.083 --> 01:24:27.875
I didn't switch sides.

1528
01:24:27.958 --> 01:24:29.417
just returning a favor.

1529
01:24:29.500 --> 01:24:31.750
- A favor?
- Yes. a favor.

1530
01:24:31.833 --> 01:24:33.708
They bailed me out of the police station.

1531
01:24:33.792 --> 01:24:35.875
The police had locked me up
for seven years.

1532
01:24:36.208 --> 01:24:38.667
- Yes. we know.
- How do you know?

1533
01:24:38.750 --> 01:24:42.375
We went to the police station
to bail you out.

1534
01:24:42.458 --> 01:24:43.500
that's where we found out.

1535
01:24:43.583 --> 01:24:45.518
Did you really go to the police station
to bail me out?

1536
01:24:45.542 --> 01:24:48.667
Of course. Do you think we woke up
early morning to have pakora?

1537
01:24:48.750 --> 01:24:50.833
Baby. leave it.

1538
01:24:51.167 --> 01:24:53.250
Tony. what is the plan?

1539
01:24:53.792 --> 01:24:56.417
The music ceremony is tomorrow.
Then the wedding follows.

1540
01:24:56.792 --> 01:24:59.083
And after sending them
on their honeymoon...

1541
01:24:59.167 --> 01:25:00.917
Hold on. Tony. What are you doing?

1542
01:25:01.000 --> 01:25:02.583
Are you not on our side at all?

1543
01:25:02.667 --> 01:25:03.708
No. Mr. Ahuja.

1544
01:25:03.792 --> 01:25:05.542
I am on your side.

1545
01:25:05.625 --> 01:25:08.458
- But I can't do what you want.
- Why?

1546
01:25:08.542 --> 01:25:12.125
Because their favor is weighing
heavily on my conscience.

1547
01:25:12.917 --> 01:25:15.500
You must've seen the tissue paper
under the paperweight.

1548
01:25:15.917 --> 01:25:18.458
It can flutter. but it can't escape.

1549
01:25:19.333 --> 01:25:21.333
That's me.

1550
01:25:21.417 --> 01:25:24.750
I feel for you.
but I can't go against them.

1551
01:25:26.208 --> 01:25:28.292
I just can't.

1552
01:25:31.000 --> 01:25:33.667
Tony needs more help than we do.

1553
01:25:34.458 --> 01:25:36.083
No. ma'am. It's the smoke.

1554
01:25:36.167 --> 01:25:38.500
You guys are going to need help.

1555
01:25:38.917 --> 01:25:41.500
Because your father
is demanding that everyone

1556
01:25:42.042 --> 01:25:43.500
be at breakfast by 9:00 a.m.

1557
01:25:43.583 --> 01:25:44.958
Including children.

1558
01:25:45.042 --> 01:25:47.250
9:00 a.m.. sharp. Army precision.

1559
01:25:47.333 --> 01:25:48.458
Brother.

1560
01:25:48.542 --> 01:25:49.542
Should we turn in?

1561
01:25:49.583 --> 01:25:51.667
Sit down.

1562
01:25:52.708 --> 01:25:54.375
Are you crazy?

1563
01:25:54.458 --> 01:25:56.542
- Are you afraid of him?
- No.

1564
01:25:56.625 --> 01:25:58.667
No need to be afraid of him.

1565
01:25:58.750 --> 01:26:00.167
This is our home.

1566
01:26:00.250 --> 01:26:02.750
not his military camp
where his orders are law.

1567
01:26:03.208 --> 01:26:05.417
See you. Mr. Ahuja.

1568
01:26:05.500 --> 01:26:06.684
Because I have to get up at eight.

1569
01:26:06.708 --> 01:26:07.875
I need an hour to get ready.

1570
01:26:07.958 --> 01:26:10.375
Where are you going. Tony?
Listen to me...

1571
01:26:10.458 --> 01:26:13.083
Please. I told you.
The tissue paper. Fluttering.

1572
01:26:13.167 --> 01:26:14.875
Don't bring me near the fire.

1573
01:26:14.958 --> 01:26:16.708
The smoke itself is suffocating me.

1574
01:26:16.792 --> 01:26:18.875
One step toward the fire.
and I'm history.

1575
01:26:19.417 --> 01:26:20.542
Good night.

1576
01:26:21.417 --> 01:26:23.125
<i>Jai Hind.</i>

1577
01:26:23.208 --> 01:26:24.708
Nine means...

1578
01:26:24.792 --> 01:26:26.583
Does he think we'll be there
if he tells us?

1579
01:26:26.667 --> 01:26:27.833
Let's see what he does.

1580
01:26:27.917 --> 01:26:28.958
Nine o'clock...

1581
01:26:29.042 --> 01:26:31.417
The call time has been announced.
Let's just go.

1582
01:26:32.458 --> 01:26:35.333
- Crazy guy. You've no reason to be afraid.
- Let's just go.

1583
01:26:36.292 --> 01:26:38.375
We're scared of no one.

1584
01:26:38.458 --> 01:26:40.833
He thinks he can get us there at nine.

1585
01:26:41.750 --> 01:26:43.500
I've faced such people fearlessly.

1586
01:26:43.583 --> 01:26:45.542
Trying to intimidate me in my own home.

1587
01:26:45.625 --> 01:26:47.708
Go fish.

1588
01:26:50.167 --> 01:26:51.333
Good morning.

1589
01:26:53.625 --> 01:26:55.708
I thought I was the first.

1590
01:26:57.250 --> 01:26:59.333
Bittu. can you sit over there?

1591
01:27:10.083 --> 01:27:11.125
Mom...

1592
01:27:11.208 --> 01:27:12.518
I showed up out of respect for you.

1593
01:27:12.542 --> 01:27:15.292
You know I don't sip water
without praying first.

1594
01:27:15.375 --> 01:27:16.958
let alone have breakfast.

1595
01:27:17.042 --> 01:27:19.250
Grandpa said
whether you have breakfast or not.

1596
01:27:19.333 --> 01:27:21.417
everyone has to be here every day at nine.

1597
01:27:21.500 --> 01:27:23.708
That's fine.
but where's the guy who called us?

1598
01:27:24.167 --> 01:27:25.292
I mean. the Captain.

1599
01:27:26.375 --> 01:27:28.167
I forgot to ask yesterday.

1600
01:27:28.625 --> 01:27:30.125
Your husband didn't come?

1601
01:27:31.208 --> 01:27:33.292
Actually. he was slightly busy.

1602
01:27:33.375 --> 01:27:35.125
so I thought I'd visit Mom.

1603
01:27:35.208 --> 01:27:38.000
Life in Singapore is pretty fast.

1604
01:27:39.292 --> 01:27:41.833
You must also be very busy.

1605
01:27:44.375 --> 01:27:45.458
Don't add sugar.

1606
01:27:46.667 --> 01:27:48.750
Vimla has tea with jaggery.

1607
01:27:56.917 --> 01:27:59.500
When was the last time you met Vimla?

1608
01:28:00.417 --> 01:28:02.417
I met her

1609
01:28:02.500 --> 01:28:05.167
two weeks before going to Malaysia.

1610
01:28:06.458 --> 01:28:08.542
Seven years. six months and 12 days ago.

1611
01:28:08.875 --> 01:28:10.708
When Avni was born.

1612
01:28:10.792 --> 01:28:12.500
You called Vimla

1613
01:28:12.583 --> 01:28:15.625
because you needed her. right?

1614
01:28:23.125 --> 01:28:26.542
Mr. Reddy. I don't have a problem
with you marrying my mom.

1615
01:28:27.292 --> 01:28:28.917
But please.

1616
01:28:29.000 --> 01:28:32.167
don't try to be my father. okay?

1617
01:28:45.417 --> 01:28:47.500
Bittu. sit over there.

1618
01:28:56.250 --> 01:28:57.333
- Tea?
- Yes.

1619
01:29:00.000 --> 01:29:01.000
Thank you.

1620
01:29:05.500 --> 01:29:06.833
Grandpa.

1621
01:29:06.917 --> 01:29:09.167
I couldn't sleep properly
all night last night.

1622
01:29:09.250 --> 01:29:10.875
Why did you wake us up so early?

1623
01:29:10.958 --> 01:29:13.250
Nights are for sleeping
and days for staying awake.

1624
01:29:13.583 --> 01:29:16.417
You're living your life the other way.

1625
01:29:16.917 --> 01:29:19.292
And also complaining about it.

1626
01:29:20.917 --> 01:29:22.375
Jeevan.

1627
01:29:22.458 --> 01:29:23.458
sit over there.

1628
01:29:23.542 --> 01:29:24.625
What do you mean?

1629
01:29:24.708 --> 01:29:26.792
Sit over there.

1630
01:29:29.375 --> 01:29:31.208
You sit over there.

1631
01:29:31.292 --> 01:29:33.125
Dad used to sit here.

1632
01:29:33.208 --> 01:29:35.292
And Dad's still going to sit there.

1633
01:29:36.708 --> 01:29:37.583
Mother-in-law

1634
01:29:37.667 --> 01:29:39.583
why aren't you saying anything?

1635
01:29:39.667 --> 01:29:40.875
Jeevan.

1636
01:29:40.958 --> 01:29:42.583
didn't you hear what Dad said?

1637
01:29:42.667 --> 01:29:43.667
Get up.

1638
01:29:55.250 --> 01:29:57.500
Come on.

1639
01:29:57.583 --> 01:29:58.583
Go.

1640
01:30:02.208 --> 01:30:03.458
Take this.

1641
01:30:11.625 --> 01:30:13.542
Good. All of you on time.

1642
01:30:13.750 --> 01:30:17.250
Lunch at two. dinner at seven.
Now. let's have breakfast.

1643
01:30:17.583 --> 01:30:18.583
Please.

1644
01:30:31.375 --> 01:30:33.417
Jeevan. since you're up.

1645
01:30:33.500 --> 01:30:35.583
go see who's at the door.

1646
01:30:39.500 --> 01:30:40.500
Go.

1647
01:30:51.917 --> 01:30:53.208
<i>My acting is okay. right?</i>

1648
01:30:53.292 --> 01:30:55.375
<i>Oh. it's absolutely great!</i>

1649
01:30:57.542 --> 01:30:59.625
<i>Everyone is very angry.</i>

1650
01:31:00.250 --> 01:31:02.000
<i>No problem.</i>

1651
01:31:02.083 --> 01:31:03.083
<i>It's okay.</i>

1652
01:31:03.125 --> 01:31:05.208
<i>I am very happy.</i>

1653
01:31:07.583 --> 01:31:10.125
What did they say?
I didn't understand a thing.

1654
01:31:10.208 --> 01:31:12.125
They are deciding
whether they will live here

1655
01:31:12.208 --> 01:31:13.488
or in Chennai after the wedding.

1656
01:31:13.542 --> 01:31:15.042
How do you know?

1657
01:31:15.125 --> 01:31:16.750
<i>You don't know?</i>

1658
01:31:17.500 --> 01:31:19.583
Kalra Sweets has a branch in Chennai.

1659
01:31:19.667 --> 01:31:21.583
Called Kalram Sweetsum on Anna Road.

1660
01:31:21.667 --> 01:31:23.750
So I know Tamil.

1661
01:31:24.292 --> 01:31:25.375
Good morning. Captain.

1662
01:31:25.667 --> 01:31:29.000
Hi. beautiful. Come. come. come.

1663
01:31:30.708 --> 01:31:31.542
Sit over there.

1664
01:31:31.625 --> 01:31:32.875
Thank you for having me.

1665
01:31:33.042 --> 01:31:35.625
- She is Tina.
- Hi Tina.

1666
01:31:36.750 --> 01:31:39.667
She's as good with the camera
as she's beautiful.

1667
01:31:39.750 --> 01:31:40.750
I'm sure.

1668
01:31:41.042 --> 01:31:42.208
Vimla.

1669
01:31:42.292 --> 01:31:44.917
she's here to click our wedding photos.

1670
01:31:45.875 --> 01:31:48.042
She is a very nice girl.

1671
01:31:48.125 --> 01:31:49.500
Captain. I have a small request.

1672
01:31:49.583 --> 01:31:52.292
My assistant missed the bus
and I need a little bit of help.

1673
01:31:52.375 --> 01:31:53.375
Okay. it will be done.

1674
01:31:53.458 --> 01:31:55.333
Tony is sitting idle.

1675
01:31:55.417 --> 01:31:56.542
He will help you out.

1676
01:31:56.625 --> 01:31:59.250
Yes. of course.
Helping people is what I do best.

1677
01:32:00.250 --> 01:32:01.559
Come on. I'll show you the location.

1678
01:32:01.583 --> 01:32:03.083
At least have breakfast.

1679
01:32:03.167 --> 01:32:05.250
I had it yesterday. you have it.

1680
01:32:05.958 --> 01:32:07.833
I really like your nature.

1681
01:32:07.958 --> 01:32:09.226
Come on. I'll show you the location.

1682
01:32:09.250 --> 01:32:10.708
- Please.
- Of course.

1683
01:32:25.583 --> 01:32:26.500
Tony. what are you doing?

1684
01:32:26.583 --> 01:32:27.583
Hey. pretty girl.

1685
01:32:28.083 --> 01:32:30.000
Why are you trying so hard?

1686
01:32:30.083 --> 01:32:31.208
I think you are forgetting.

1687
01:32:31.292 --> 01:32:33.958
No matter what you do.
your wish will never come true.

1688
01:32:34.583 --> 01:32:35.583
You see. Kannu.

1689
01:32:35.625 --> 01:32:38.875
life should be lived
according to needs.

1690
01:32:38.958 --> 01:32:40.583
not wishes.

1691
01:32:40.667 --> 01:32:42.792
Because needs are always fulfilled.

1692
01:32:42.875 --> 01:32:46.167
And even an emperor's wishes
remain unfulfilled.

1693
01:32:46.250 --> 01:32:48.083
Is it? And what about you?

1694
01:32:48.167 --> 01:32:49.667
In my case.

1695
01:32:49.750 --> 01:32:51.667
I'll consider myself an emperor.

1696
01:32:51.750 --> 01:32:52.792
Tony.

1697
01:32:52.875 --> 01:32:54.708
Hey. sweetheart.

1698
01:32:55.083 --> 01:32:57.458
Welcome in my heart.

1699
01:32:58.000 --> 01:32:59.250
Tina. where were you?

1700
01:32:59.333 --> 01:33:01.167
I looked all over for you.

1701
01:33:01.333 --> 01:33:02.684
You're looking the prettiest girl
in the party.

1702
01:33:02.708 --> 01:33:04.792
Let's click a picture... with you.

1703
01:33:10.792 --> 01:33:12.667
Looking so beautiful. mom.

1704
01:33:13.250 --> 01:33:14.292
Thank you.

1705
01:33:17.000 --> 01:33:18.000
Mom

1706
01:33:18.792 --> 01:33:20.333
are you angry with me?

1707
01:33:22.208 --> 01:33:25.000
How can I be angry with you?
You're here for only two days.

1708
01:33:25.875 --> 01:33:26.875
After that

1709
01:33:28.583 --> 01:33:30.042
you'll leave too.

1710
01:33:30.542 --> 01:33:32.625
and maybe me too.

1711
01:33:33.750 --> 01:33:35.833
Who knows whether we'll meet again.

1712
01:33:37.042 --> 01:33:38.042
Anyway...

1713
01:33:39.042 --> 01:33:41.250
Mr. Reddy is going through your papers.

1714
01:33:41.333 --> 01:33:43.750
I will sign them before you leave.

1715
01:33:46.125 --> 01:33:48.208
Where did you meet with Mr. Reddy?

1716
01:33:48.542 --> 01:33:52.042
You already know… if people are meant
for each other. they find their way.

1717
01:33:52.375 --> 01:33:54.458
You know very well.

1718
01:33:55.000 --> 01:33:56.458
How about you?

1719
01:33:56.542 --> 01:33:59.583
Are you doing okay?

1720
01:34:00.208 --> 01:34:01.583
Yes. all good.

1721
01:34:01.667 --> 01:34:03.292
How is Abhinav?

1722
01:34:03.375 --> 01:34:04.375
He's great.

1723
01:34:05.667 --> 01:34:08.000
I wish he could come...

1724
01:34:08.083 --> 01:34:10.458
Mom. I'll go check if Avni's ready or not.

1725
01:34:10.542 --> 01:34:11.750
I'll talk to you later.

1726
01:34:15.958 --> 01:34:18.083
Brother. The guests are arriving.

1727
01:34:18.625 --> 01:34:19.706
The ambiance is picking up.

1728
01:34:20.417 --> 01:34:22.375
Sit here. Sit down.

1729
01:34:23.417 --> 01:34:25.542
Arriving guests.
picking up ambiance...

1730
01:34:27.417 --> 01:34:29.542
Are you enjoying it?
You're peeking a lot.

1731
01:34:32.250 --> 01:34:33.250
Hello.

1732
01:34:33.833 --> 01:34:35.250
You guys are not ready yet.

1733
01:34:35.333 --> 01:34:36.434
The music ceremony begins soon.

1734
01:34:36.458 --> 01:34:38.083
No one invited us.

1735
01:34:38.167 --> 01:34:39.792
Ms. Vimla must have forgotten.

1736
01:34:39.875 --> 01:34:42.333
With all the people around.
it slips one's mind.

1737
01:34:42.917 --> 01:34:45.000
You can come as my guests.

1738
01:34:46.583 --> 01:34:48.333
Check this out. Naag.

1739
01:34:48.417 --> 01:34:50.750
We're now guests of our
own guests in our own home.

1740
01:34:52.250 --> 01:34:54.875
In fact. Tony. don't go anywhere.

1741
01:34:55.208 --> 01:34:58.208
Come sit here. and let's enjoy ourselves.

1742
01:34:58.667 --> 01:34:59.500
Yes. Tony.

1743
01:34:59.583 --> 01:35:02.125
You should support us
at a time like this. Sit down.

1744
01:35:02.208 --> 01:35:04.625
Even if I sit here. ma'am.

1745
01:35:04.708 --> 01:35:06.500
the wedding is still on.

1746
01:35:06.583 --> 01:35:08.667
Let me enjoy the snacks.

1747
01:35:09.167 --> 01:35:10.917
Even strangers are enjoying it.

1748
01:35:11.000 --> 01:35:12.333
In fact. come with me.

1749
01:35:12.417 --> 01:35:13.542
No.

1750
01:35:13.625 --> 01:35:15.708
Can I say something. Mr. Ahuja?

1751
01:35:16.083 --> 01:35:18.375
You are responsible for driving her away.

1752
01:35:19.583 --> 01:35:23.083
Because she thinks Mr. Reddy
loves her more than all of you.

1753
01:35:24.250 --> 01:35:26.333
You show resentment several times a day.

1754
01:35:26.417 --> 01:35:27.583
Ever shown her love?

1755
01:35:27.667 --> 01:35:29.333
Have you?

1756
01:35:29.417 --> 01:35:31.167
We are her children.

1757
01:35:31.250 --> 01:35:33.167
Why do we have to show her our love?

1758
01:35:33.250 --> 01:35:35.542
Mothers don't have any obligation.

1759
01:35:35.875 --> 01:35:37.958
But they still show their love.

1760
01:35:38.333 --> 01:35:40.500
But it's okay. I understand.

1761
01:35:40.583 --> 01:35:41.667
What are you eating?

1762
01:35:41.750 --> 01:35:42.667
Peanuts.

1763
01:35:42.750 --> 01:35:44.667
How about snacks? Fresh from the oven.

1764
01:35:44.750 --> 01:35:46.833
Who is handling the catering?

1765
01:35:48.542 --> 01:35:50.292
Kalra Sweets.

1766
01:35:50.375 --> 01:35:51.375
Tony...

1767
01:35:51.417 --> 01:35:54.042
If we don't handle
family weddings. who will?

1768
01:35:55.500 --> 01:35:58.542
You guys enjoy peanuts and <i>Bhujia</i>.

1769
01:35:59.167 --> 01:36:00.167
See you.

1770
01:36:02.958 --> 01:36:03.875
Brother.

1771
01:36:03.958 --> 01:36:07.125
Reddy the cheat is out there
holding hands with a gorgeous lady.

1772
01:36:07.208 --> 01:36:08.917
- What?
- Yes.

1773
01:36:09.000 --> 01:36:11.083
Whose hand is he holding?

1774
01:36:11.875 --> 01:36:13.958
Let me see.

1775
01:36:16.667 --> 01:36:18.458
Idiot.

1776
01:36:18.542 --> 01:36:20.625
That's Mom.

1777
01:36:24.208 --> 01:36:27.792
<i>♪ Are you hiding a secret in your heart?
Why so quiet! ♪</i>

1778
01:36:27.875 --> 01:36:31.500
<i>♪ Better speak up now
It's the auspicious night ♪</i>

1779
01:36:35.083 --> 01:36:38.625
<i>♪ Take my advice
And don't stop your feet ♪</i>

1780
01:36:38.708 --> 01:36:43.208
<i>♪ Hey DJ. check this beat ♪</i>

1781
01:36:44.000 --> 01:36:47.500
<i>♪ My moves are priceless
You'll be spellbound ♪</i>

1782
01:36:47.583 --> 01:36:51.167
<i>♪ There's going to be some push
And shove. better watch out ♪</i>

1783
01:36:51.250 --> 01:36:54.792
<i>♪ Let the eyes do the talking
Hand in hand. slowly walking ♪</i>

1784
01:36:54.875 --> 01:36:58.667
<i>♪ Guys wait to do it with me ♪</i>

1785
01:36:58.750 --> 01:37:02.333
<i>♪ A Punjabi beat plays
The uncles dance in their seat ♪</i>

1786
01:37:02.417 --> 01:37:05.917
<i>♪ Aunt's calling you on the floor ♪</i>

1787
01:37:06.000 --> 01:37:11.708
<i>♪ Be a little flirtatious
And a little gentle ♪</i>

1788
01:37:12.125 --> 01:37:15.667
<i>♪ Don't be sentimental. I'll go mental ♪</i>

1789
01:37:15.750 --> 01:37:19.333
<i>♪ Don't be sentimental. I'll go mental ♪</i>

1790
01:37:19.417 --> 01:37:24.167
<i>♪ Don't be sentimental. I'll go mental ♪</i>

1791
01:37:46.250 --> 01:37:53.167
<i>♪ The bride let out a whistle.
And the vibe turned to fun ♪</i>

1792
01:37:53.542 --> 01:38:00.125
<i>♪ Her electric swag
Easily topped everyone ♪</i>

1793
01:38:00.792 --> 01:38:05.333
<i>♪ Watching you sway
Makes my heart lose control ♪</i>

1794
01:38:05.417 --> 01:38:07.958
<i>♪ Makes my heart lose control ♪</i>

1795
01:38:08.042 --> 01:38:13.667
<i>♪ These Desi moves on a Gen Z beat</i> ♪

1796
01:38:13.750 --> 01:38:16.292
♪ <i>Rock my soul ♪</i>

1797
01:38:16.375 --> 01:38:19.958
<i>♪ The glow on your face
The flow of your dress ♪</i>

1798
01:38:20.042 --> 01:38:24.125
<i>♪ Drives me crazy slowly slow ♪</i>

1799
01:38:24.208 --> 01:38:30.250
<i>♪ Be romantic. why are you being gentle! ♪</i>

1800
01:38:30.333 --> 01:38:33.958
<i>♪ Don't be sentimental. I'll go mental ♪</i>

1801
01:38:34.042 --> 01:38:37.542
<i>♪ Don't be sentimental. I'll go mental ♪</i>

1802
01:38:37.625 --> 01:38:42.333
<i>♪ Don't be sentimental. I'll go mental ♪</i>

1803
